%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mystery%20Respiratory%20Disease%20Spreads%20Across%20China%2C%20Indian%20Doctor's%20Warning%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20reported%20outbreak%20of%20H9N2%20cases%20and%20clusters%20of%20respiratory%20illness%20in%20children%20in%20northern%20China%2C%20Ram%20Manohar%20Lohia%20Hospital%20Director%20Dr%20Ajay%20Shukla%20advised%20people%20to%20be%20careful%2C%20follow%20routine%20practices%20of%20cleanness%20and%20if%20there's%20someone%20who%20has%20got%20this%20respiratory%20illness%20or%20infection%20they%20should%20try%20to%20maintain%20distance%20from%20other%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20just%20advise%20people%20to%20be%20careful.%20Follow%20routine%20practices%20of%20cleanness%20and%20if%20you%20feel%20that%20there's%20someone%20who's%20got%20this%20respiratory%20illness%20or%20infection%2C%20since%20a%20lot%20of%20these%20cases%20are%20viral%20and%20they%20can%20be%20transmitted%2C%20try%20to%20maintain%20distance%20from%20other%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Shukla%20said%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20advice%20comes%20after%20an%20undetermined%20pneumonia%20outbreak%20in%20China%20is%20hitting%20children%20hard%2C%20with%20media%20reports%20describing%20overwhelmed%20children's%20hospitals%20in%20multiple%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20we%20are%20also%20dealing%20with%20pollution%20if%20you're%20going%20out%2C%20and%20if%20you%20can%20afford%20it%2C%20it's%20better%20you%20should%20use%20a%20mask%2C%20preferably%20an%20N95%20and%20N99%20mask.%20Wash%20your%20hands%20and%20maintain%20safe%2C%20healthy%20practices%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20exercising%20precautions%20among%20children%20Dr%20Shukla%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20children%20are%20going%20to%20school%2C%20then%20take%20special%20care%20that%20they%20do%20not%20have%20cough%2C%20cold%2C%20fever%20or%20any%20other%20symptoms%2C%20and%20talk%20to%20them%20and%20ask%20if%20any%20child%20in%20their%20class%20is%20sick%2C%20and%20if%20this%20happens%2C%20inform%20the%20school%20teacher%20about%20it%20and%20if%20your%20child%20is%20sick%20then%20do%20not%20send%20him%20to%20school.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Shukla%20said%20that%20the%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20small%20children%20going%20to%20hospitals%20with%20respiratory%20illnesses%20has%20disrupted%20the%20situation%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20early%20I%20would%20say%20the%20amount%20of%20information%20that%20we%20are%20able%20to%20access%20is%20very%2C%20very%20little.%20The%20WHO%20is%20definitely%20very%20much%20concerned%20about%20it.%20And%2C%20it%20is%20trying%20to%20get%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20authorities%20in%20China%20to%20extract%20as%20maximum%20details%20as%20possible.%20But%20so%20far%20the%20picture%20that%20is%20coming%20out%2C%20is%20that%20there%20is%20a%20great%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20small%20children%20going%20into%20hospitals%20with%20respiratory%20illnesses%2C%20and%20in%20a%20few%20centres%2C%20they%20have%20reported%20an%20increase%20of%20almost%201200%20children%20a%20day%20which%20is%20a%20huge%20number%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20schools%20have%20told%20children%20not%20to%20come%20to%20their%20classes%20inside%20the%20school.%20So%20the%20situation%20is%20definitely%20been%20disrupted%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Ajay%20Shukla%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Shukla%20said%20that%20because%20of%20COVID%20and%20stringent%20lockdowns%20the%20immunity%20in%20the%20general%20population%20and%20children%20has%20been%20impacted%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20rebound%20in%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20the%20limited%20information%20that%20is%20available%2C%20a%20few%20experts%20have%20given%20opinions%20about%20the%20increase%20in%20infection%20in%20children.%20According%20to%20one%20expert%2C%20because%20of%20COVID.%20And%20because%20of%20the%20very%20stringent%20lockdowns%20that%20we%20saw%20in%20China%2C%20the%20immunity%20in%20the%20general%20population%20and%20the%20children%20over%20there%20has%20been%20impacted%20and%20because%20of%20that%20low%20immunity%2C%20this%20rebound%20in%20cases%20is%20being%20seen%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Shukla%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%20requested%20detailed%20information%20from%20China%20on%20an%20increase%20in%20respiratory%20illnesses%20and%20pneumonia%20among%20the%20country's%20children%2C%20using%20language%20similar%20to%20a%20Jan.%205%2C%202020%2C%20pre-pandemic%20missive%20regarding%20COVID-19.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20another%20expert%2C%20it's%20most%20probably%20just%20a%20bacterial%20infection%20or%20a%20viral%20infection.%20Some%20organism%20by%20the%20name%20of%20MIKO%20plasma%20pneumoniae%2C%20which%20is%20common%20and%20not%20a%20dangerous%20bacterial%20infection%20is%20probably%20at%20the%20root%20of%20this%20illness.%20This%20has%20led%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20cases%20and%20it's%20basically%20because%20of%20the%20low%20immunity%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20severe%20lockdown%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Shukla%20added%20that%20experts%20have%20also%20said%20that%20there%20is%20no%20need%20to%20worry%20about%20the%20disease%20in%20India%20as%20its%20symptoms%20have%20not%20been%20seen%20in%20the%20country%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20a%20single%20patient%20infected%20with%20this%20disease%20has%20been%20found%20in%20India%20yet.%20There%20is%20no%20increase%20in%20cases%20in%20any%20part%20of%20India%20so%20far%2C%20or%20any%20part%20of%20the%20world%20apart%20from%20China.%20So%20all%20the%20cases%20that%20we're%20hearing%20are%20from%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20doctor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Director%20of%20RML%20Hospital%20said%20that%20earlier%2020%20to%2030%20children%20came%20to%20the%20hospital%20every%20day%2C%20but%20now%20their%20number%20is%20less%20as%2010%20to%2015%20children%20are%20coming%20to%20the%20hospital.%20The%20number%20of%20children%20with%20respiratory%20diseases%20is%20not%20much%2C%20he%20said%20adding%20that%20there%20is%20no%20patient%20suffering%20from%20this%20disease%20in%20his%20hospital%20at%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Shukla%20asked%20people%20not%20to%20panic%20and%20that%20a%20pandemic-like%20situation%20will%20not%20happen%20going%20by%20the%20limited%20information%20that%20exists%20about%20this%20new%20influenza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20the%20very%20few%20details%20that%20are%20available%2C%20people%20are%20saying%20there's%20nothing%20to%20panic%20about%2C%20there's%20nothing%20to%20suggest%20it%20is%20something%20that%20will%20take%20the%20shape%20of%20a%20pandemic%2C%20like%20with%20COVID.%20So%2C%20we%20should%20not%20start%20comparing%20it%20with%20that.%20I%20would%20suggest%20that%20we%20need%20to%20monitor%20the%20situation%20very%20closely%20and%20wait%20for%20additional%20information%20before%20we%20reach%20any%20conclusion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RML%20Hospital%20Director%20said%20that%20there%20is%20normally%20an%20increasing%20number%20of%20influenza%20cases%20before%20the%20winter%20every%20year%20and%20this%20does%20not%20suggest%20an%20abnormal%20increase%20in%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20see%20every%20winter%20because%20of%20the%20cold%20and%20because%20of%20the%20pollution%2C%20there's%20always%20an%20increasing%20number%20of%20cases%2C%20especially%20respiratory%20illnesses%2C%20we%20see%20an%20increase%20so%20I%20mean%2C%20that%20increase%20is%20bound%20to%20happen%20because%20we've%20not%20really%20felt%20the%20winter%20so%20far.%20So%20those%20cases%20are%20going%20to%20increase.%20I%20don't%20think%20there's%20any%20reason%20why%20we%20should%20feel%20that%20we%20will%20have%20an%20increase%20beyond%20that%20increase%20which%20is%20seen%20every%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Shukla%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700887380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fe8ul6shg_china-reuters_625x300_23_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdoctor-warns-amid-respiratory-illness-outbreak-in-china-4604242%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20reported%20outbreak%20of%20H9N2%20cases%20and%20clusters%20of%20respiratory%20illness%20in%20children%20in%20northern%20China%2C%20Ram%20Manohar%20Lohia%20Hospital%20Director%20Dr%20Ajay%20Shukla%20advised%20people%20to%20be%20careful%2C%20follow%20routine%20practices%20of%20cleanness.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdoctor-warns-amid-respiratory-illness-outbreak-in-china-4604242%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdoctor-warns-amid-respiratory-illness-outbreak-in-china-4604242%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdoctor-warns-amid-respiratory-illness-outbreak-in-china-4604242%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Teen%20Queer%20Artist%20Dies%20By%20Suicide%20After%20Hate%20Comments%20On%20Reel%2C%20Claims%20Actor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2016-year-old%20queer%20artist%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Ujjain%20died%20by%20suicide%20following%20thousands%20of%20hate%20comments%20on%20an%20Instagram%20reel%20the%20artist%20posted%2C%20claimed%20an%20actor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPranshu%2C%20a%2016-year-old%20queer%20artist%20from%20Ujjain%2C%20was%20a%20self-taught%20makeup%20artist%20from%20Ujjain%20and%20ran%20an%20Instagram%20handle%20where%20they%20posted%20makeup%20and%20beauty%20content.%20On%20Diwali%2C%20The%2016-year-old%20posted%20an%20Instagram%20transition%20reel%20in%20a%20saree.%3C%2Fp%3E%