20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105488015.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EYoni%20Ashner%2C%20an%20Israeli%20national%20whose%20wife%20and%20two%20daughters%20returned%20to%20him%20after%20being%20held%20hostage%20by%20Hamas%20for%2049%20days%2C%20has%20said%20that%20he%20won't%20be%20celebrating%20the%20release%20unless%20all%20the%20hostages%20under%20captivity%20return%20to%20their%20loved%20ones%2C%20Times%20of%20Israel%20reported.%20Asher's%20wife%2C%20Doron%2C%20and%20their%20two%20young%20daughters%20Raz%20(5)%20and%20Aviv%20(2)%20were%20taken%20on%20October%207%20from%20the%20sealed%20room%20in%20Kibbutz%20Nir%20Oz%2C%20near%20Gaza.%20Ashner%20thanked%20the%20Israeli%20government%20and%20IDF%20and%20those%20working%20to%20get%20the%20hostages%20back.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fyoni-ashner-whose-family-was-freed-from-hamas-wont-celebrate-till-all-hostages-return%2Farticleshow%2F105488015.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fyoni-ashner-whose-family-was-freed-from-hamas-wont-celebrate-till-all-hostages-return%2Famp_articleshow%2F105488015.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fyoni-ashner-whose-family-was-freed-from-hamas-wont-celebrate-till-all-hostages-return%2Famp_articleshow%2F105488015.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Made%20Israel%20Push%20Harder%20For%20Return%20Of%20Hostages%20Held%20Captive%20By%20Hamas%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20of%20the%20first%20group%20of%20Israeli%20women%20and%20children%20taken%20hostage%20by%20Hamas%20is%20-%20at%20least%20in%20part%20-%20the%20result%20of%20an%20intense%20campaign%20waged%20by%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20night%20of%20the%20Oct.%207%20assault%2C%20during%20which%20Hamas%20militants%20killed%201%2C200%20Israelis%20and%20kidnapped%20240%20others%2C%20the%20government%20of%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20spoke%20of%20a%20single%20goal%3A%20%26quot%3Bthe%20destruction%20of%20the%20military%20and%20governmental%20capabilities%20of%20Hamas%20and%20Palestinian%20Islamic%20Jihad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20days%20later%2C%20hostages%20were%20again%20left%20unmentioned%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20alongside%20war%20cabinet%20chiefs.%20It%20took%20two%20more%20weeks%20for%20Netanyahu%20to%20say%20out%20loud%3A%20%26quot%3Bwe%20have%20set%20two%20goals%20for%20the%20war%3A%20eliminate%20Hamas%20and%20do%20everything%20possible%20to%20return%20our%20hostages%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shift%20was%20driven%20by%20family%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20key%20player%20was%20Avichai%20Brodutch%2C%20whose%20wife%20and%20three%20young%20children%20were%20abducted.%20He%20scrawled%20a%20homemade%20sign%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20Family%20is%20in%20Gaza%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20stood%20alone%20outside%20the%20Defense%20Ministry%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%2C%20attracting%20a%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Dudi%20Zalmanovich%2C%20a%20powerful%20lawyer%20with%20a%20relative%20taken%20to%20Gaza%2C%20and%20Ronen%20Zur%2C%20a%20public%20relations%20guru%2C%20established%20the%20%26quot%3BHostages%20and%20Missing%20Families%20Forum.%26quot%3B%20They%20gathered%20information%20and%20set%20up%20a%20data%20base%2C%20soon%20joined%20by%20former%20spy%20and%20security%20chiefs%2C%20celebrities%20and%20film%20directors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Hostage%20Square'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20'hostage%20square'%20was%20set%20up%20across%20from%20where%20the%20government%20was%20meeting.%20Outside%20the%20Tel%20Aviv%20Museum%20of%20Art%2C%20tables%20were%20set%20up%20with%20240%20empty%20places%20for%20a%20Shabbat%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHuge%20billboards%20with%20hostage%20photos%20cropped%20up%20on%20every%20corner%20as%20well%20as%20in%20New%20York's%20Times%20Square%20and%20other%20international%20cities.%20Three%20floors%20of%20an%20office%20building%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%20became%20a%20headquarters%20for%20the%20families.%20They%20walked%20for%20four%20days%20from%20the%20city%20to%20Jerusalem%20joined%20by%20thousands%2C%20disrupting%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20a%20few%20hundred%20volunteers%20within%20days%2C%20and%20now%20have%20between%201%2C000%20and%201%2C500%2C%20some%20working%20full%20time%20and%20some%20a%20few%20hours%20a%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Daniel%20Shek%2C%20a%20former%20Israeli%20ambassador%20to%20France.%20He%20heads%20the%20group's%20diplomatic%20relations%20and%20has%20sent%20delegations%20to%20Greece%2C%20the%20US%2C%20Canada%2C%20Belgium%20and%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDozens%20of%20the%20hostages%20are%20dual%20nationals%20and%20the%20goal%20has%20been%20to%20get%20foreign%20officials%20to%20pressure%20Netanyahu.%20Gili%20Roman%2C%20whose%20sister%20Yarden%20holds%20a%20German%20passport%20and%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20held%20in%20Gaza%2C%20went%20to%20Berlin%20and%20met%20with%20Chancellor%20Olaf%20Scholz.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20first%20couple%20of%20weeks%2C%20the%20number%20one%20priority%20was%20beating%20Hamas%2C%20winning%20the%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20Shek%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20pushed%20for%20the%20priority%20to%20be%20the%20hostages.%20We%20may%20have%20played%20a%20role%2C%20and%20I%20am%20proud%20of%20what%20we%20did.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGround%20Troops%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20being%20released%20now%20are%20among%20the%20more%20than%2030%20children%20and%20dozens%20of%20women%20taken%20when%20Hamas%20operatives%20broke%20through%20the%20border%20to%20Israel%20and%20shot%20their%20way%20into%20the%20neighboring%20communities%2C%20killing%20and%20abducting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20several%20weeks%20of%20punishing%20air%20attacks%20by%20Israel%20in%20its%20war%20on%20Hamas%2C%20the%20question%20arose%20of%20sending%20in%20ground%20troops%2C%20but%20many%20feared%20that%20would%20endanger%20the%20hostages.%20Netanyahu%20and%20his%20defense%20chiefs%20argued%20that%20the%20way%20to%20persuade%20Hamas%20to%20yield%20hostages%20was%20to%20pressure%20them%20militarily.%20This%20was%20their%20way%20of%20joining%20the%20war's%20two%20goals%20into%20one%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20war%20is%20aimed%20at%20destroying%20the%20Hamas%20infrastructure%2C%20much%20of%20which%20is%20underground%20in%20tunnels%2C%20where%20hostages%20are%20presumed%20to%20be%20held.%20In%20the%20process%2C%20it%20has%20killed%20more%20than%2013%2C000%20Gazans%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Hamas-run%20health%20ministry%2C%20and%20reduced%20much%20of%20the%20crowded%20seaside%20strip%20to%20near%20rubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20toll%20that%20has%20shocked%20many%20abroad.%20Israel%20blames%20Hamas%20for%20operating%20among%20its%20civilians%20and%20says%20the%20war%20must%20be%20brought%20to%20a%20conclusion%20to%20prevent%20a%20repeat%20of%20what%20happened%20on%20Oct.%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20exchange%20for%2050%20Israeli%20hostages%20to%20be%20released%20over%20the%20coming%20three%20days%2C%20Israel%20is%20permitting%20truckloads%20of%20humanitarian%20aide%20and%20freeing%20150%20Palestinian%20women%20and%20minors%20it%20holds%20in%20its%20own%20prisons.%20Hamas%2C%20which%20is%20considered%20a%20terrorist%20organization%20by%20the%20US%20and%20European%20Union%2C%20can%20extend%20the%20truce%20by%20a%20day%20for%20each%20additional%2010%20hostages%20it%20releases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20in%20Israel%20have%20argued%20that%20the%20authorities%20should%2C%20if%20needed%2C%20offer%20to%20release%20all%206%2C000%20Palestinians%20it%20holds%20in%20prison%20to%20get%20their%20hostages%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20seems%20little%20likelihood%20of%20that%20happening.%20The%20last%20time%20Israel%20released%20a%20huge%20number%20of%20prisoners%20in%20exchange%20for%20one%20of%20its%20own%2C%20among%20those%20released%20was%20Yahya%20Sinwar.%20He's%20been%20the%20head%20of%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%20for%20the%20past%20five%20years%20and%20viewed%20by%20Israel%20as%20the%20mastermind%20of%20the%20Oct.%207%20massacre.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700884800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fsu4tagd_benjamin-netanyahu-reuters_625x300_02_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-made-netanyahu-push-harder-for-return-of-israeli-hostages-from-gaza-4604391%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20release%20of%20the%20first%20group%20of%20Israeli%20women%20and%20children%20taken%20hostage%20by%20Hamas%20is%20-%20at%20least%20in%20part%20-%20the%20result%20of%20an%20intense%20campaign%20waged%20by%20their%20families.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-made-netanyahu-push-harder-for-return-of-israeli-hostages-from-gaza-4604391%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-made-netanyahu-push-harder-for-return-of-israeli-hostages-from-gaza-4604391%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-made-netanyahu-push-harder-for-return-of-israeli-hostages-from-gaza-4604391%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2244th%20Blue%20Dragon%20Film%20Awards%20winners%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700884210000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105487868%2Cimgsize-42814.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2