gan%20their%20first%20joint%20sea%20and%20air%20patrols%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%2C%20joining%20the%20U.S.%20in%20efforts%20to%20counter%20China's%20aggressive%20activities.%20China%20claims%20almost%20the%20entire%20South%20China%20Sea%2C%20but%20the%20Permanent%20Court%20of%20Arbitration%20in%202016%20ruled%20against%20China's%20claims.%20The%20joint%20patrols%20by%20the%20Philippines%20and%20Australia%20aim%20to%20underscore%20their%20commitment%20to%20a%20rules-based%20order.%20The%20patrols%20will%20take%20place%20in%20the%20West%20Philippine%20Sea.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fphilippines-australia-start-sea-air-patrols-in-south-china-sea%2Farticleshow%2F105487706.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fphilippines-australia-start-sea-air-patrols-in-south-china-sea%2Famp_articleshow%2F105487706.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fphilippines-australia-start-sea-air-patrols-in-south-china-sea%2Famp_articleshow%2F105487706.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCongress%20Will%20Get%20Another%20Chance%26quot%3B%3A%20Sachin%20Pilot%20As%20Rajasthan%20Votes%20Today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Sachin%20Pilot%20exuded%20confidence%20on%20Saturday%20that%20his%20party%20will%20get%20another%20chance%20in%20the%20state%2C%20saying%20the%20mood%20of%20the%20people%20is%20towards%20changing%20the%20trend%20of%20alternating%20governments%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20ANI%20about%20the%20polls%2C%20the%20former%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20the%20state%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20confident%20that%20Congress%20will%20get%20another%20chance%20in%20the%20state%20(to%20return%20to%20power).%20We%20will%20get%20the%20numbers%20required%20to%20form%20the%20government.%20People%20here%20want%20to%20vote%20for%20those%20who%20deliver%20and%20stay%20committed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20mood%20of%20the%20people%20here%20is%20towards%20changing%20the%20trend%20of%20alternating%20governments%20this%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20played%20down%20the%20apparent%20rift%20with%20Rajasthan%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20worked%20together%20(for%20the%20party).%20It%20is%20not%20about%20two%20or%20three%20people.%20The%20Congress%20unit%20of%20Rajasthan%20is%20united%2C%26quot%3B%20Pilot%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20began%20in%20199%20out%20of%20200%20assembly%20seats%20in%20Rajasthan%20on%20Saturday%20after%20days%20of%20hectic%20campaigning%20by%20major%20political%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20ruling%20Congress%20and%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElections%20in%20the%20Karanpur%20constituency%20were%20adjourned%20due%20to%20the%20passing%20of%20Congress%20candidate%20Gurmeet%20Singh%20Koonar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20polling%20began%20at%207%20am%20and%20voters%20can%20cast%20their%20ballots%20until%206%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdequate%20security%20arrangements%20have%20been%20made%20to%20ensure%20peaceful%20and%20fair%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%201%2C02%2C290%20security%20personnel%20have%20been%20deployed%20to%20ensure%20peaceful%20voting.%20A%20total%20force%20of%2069%2C114%20police%20personnel%2C%2032%2C876%20Rajasthan%20Home%20Guard%2C%20Forest%20Guard%20and%20RAC%20personnel%20have%20been%20deployed%20and%20700%20companies%20of%20CAPF%20have%20been%20deployed%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20counting%20of%20votes%20will%20be%20taken%20up%20on%20December%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20the%20Congress%20won%2099%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20won%2073.%20Gehlot%20assumed%20the%20CM%20position%20with%20the%20support%20of%20BSP%20MLAs%20and