ation%20into%20Apple%20security%20notifications%20and%20newer%20data%20breaches%20and%20security%20incidents%20that%20are%20being%20reported%20every%20week.%20CERT-IN%20as%20a%20cyber%20security%20regulator%20has%20been%20non-performing%20%E2%80%93%20and%20with%20exemptions%20under%20RTI%2C%20it%20will%20be%20even%20harder%20to%20demand%20transparency%20from%20an%20already%20secretive%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20week%20saw%20multiple%20cyber%20security%20incidents%2C%20with%20updates%20about%20Apple%20security%20incidents%20to%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2Fvirus-apple-threat-notification-official-says-9039800%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20an%20anonymous%20official%20claiming%20it%20was%20likely%20a%20virus%20that%20was%20the%20cause%20behind%20Apple%E2%80%99s%20security%20notifications.%20There%20is%20no%20logic%20or%20proof%20for%20this%20claim%20from%20CERT-IN%2C%20which%20has%20never%20shared%20any%20forensic%20reports%20in%20the%20past%20either.%20Exemptions%20from%20RTI%20now%20even%20make%20it%20hard%20for%20people%20to%20demand%20documentation%20to%20this%20effect%20from%20CERT-IN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20continuous%20data%20breaches%20that%20have%20been%20reported%20in%20the%20past%2C%20CERT-IN%20was%20never%20serious%20about%20providing%20a%20response%20to%20cybersecurity%20incidents.%20A%20report%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Ftech%2Ftechnology%2Ftaj-hotels-data-breach-may-have-exposed-1-5-million-source%2Farticleshow%2F105439086.cms%5C%22%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20claimed%20Taj%20Hotels%20suffered%20a%20data%20breach%20pertaining%20to%201.5%20million%20customers%2C%20with%20the%20threat%20actor%20who%20has%20put%20data%20up%20for%20sale%20on%20BreachForums%20%E2%80%93%20a%20dark%20web%20marketplace.%20CERT-IN%20has%20been%20made%20aware%20of%20this%20incident%2C%20but%20what%20it%20does%20to%20handle%20this%20security%20incident%20will%20be%20unknown%2C%20just%20like%20the%20previous%20data%20breaches%20it%20never%20responded%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20all%20of%20these%20incidents%2C%20there%20is%20yet%20another%20actor%20claiming%20to%20be%20selling%20backdoor%20access%20to%20the%20finance%20ministry%20web%20server.%20A%20screenshot%20shared%20by%20DailyDarkWeb%20shows%20a%20threat%20actor%20with%20details%20of%20the%20linux%20server%20and%20the%20storage%20capacity%2C%20selling%20access%20to%20it%20for%20%242%2C500.%20While%20there%20are%20many%20reported%20breaches%20on%20various%20marketplaces%20across%20the%20web%2C%20CERT-IN%20is%20missing%20in%20action%20in%20responding%20to%20these%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FIndia%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23India%3C%2Fa%3E%20%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3%20%E2%80%93%20Allegedly%2C%20Unauthorized%20access%20to%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%20(India)%20is%20on%20sale%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrice%3A%20%242500%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FDarkWeb%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23DarkWeb%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2Faccess%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23access%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FV8FuuYIr3d%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FV8FuuYIr3d%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Daily%20Dark%20Web%20(%40DailyDarkWeb)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDailyDarkWeb%2Fstatus%2F1727386462323421341%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2022%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20CERT-IN%20has%20the%20intent%20to%20respond%20to%20these%20incidents%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20either%20the%20resources%20or%20the%20personnel%20to%20help%20achieve%20this.%20Because%20CERT-IN%20regulates%20the%20industry%20at%20large%20by%20empanelling%20cyber%20security%20agencies%2C%20all%20of%20the%20cybersecurity%20expertise%20is%20with%20the%20private%20sector.%20With%20not%20enough%20funding%20to%20hire%20people%2C%20it%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%20get%20the%20people%20and%20tools%20it%20needs%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fhigh-court%2Fdelhi-high-court%2Fdelhi-high-court-rejects-plea-against-indian-computer-emergency-response-team-empanelment-procedure-cybersecurity-firms-242700%5C%22%3Eorganisation%20approached%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20CERT-IN%E2%80%99s%20empanelment%20guidelines%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20transparency%20in%20the%20process.%20The%20court%20dismissed%20the%20petition%2C%20saying%20the%20court%20can%E2%80%99t%20get%20into%20an%20extremely%20technical%20process%20of%20empanelment%20and%20substitute%20it%20with%20its%20own%20conclusion.%20While%20the%20evolution%20of%20jurisprudence%20related%20to%20technology%20is%20a%20separate%20matter%20in%20itself%2C%20CERT-IN%20as%20the%20technical%20expert%20pretty%20much%20determines%20what%20would%20be%20considered%20evidence%20with%20its%20hold%20on%20empanelment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20India%20has%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20bug%20bounty%20hackers%2C%20who%20routinely%20report%20security%20issues%20to%20large%20organisations%20across%20the%20world%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20CERT-IN%20they%20pretty%20much%20receive%20no%20active%20response%20for%20reporting%20security%20incidents.%20There%20is%20no%20incentive%20for%20security%20researchers%20to%20report%20incidents%20to%20CERT-IN.%20India%20has%20all%20the%20talent%20and%20resources%20it%20needs%20to%20fix%20cybersecurity%20problems%2C%20but%20there%20is%20no%20intent.%20Security%20through%20obscurity%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20work%20well%20for%20cyberspace%2C%20yet%20this%20is%20what%20is%20practised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20economic%20landscape%20of%20cybersecurity%20in%20India%20is%20very%20inter-linked%20to%20CERT-IN%20and%20its%20policies%3B%20the%20state%20is%20determining%20how%20this%20industry%20functions%20and%20it%20wants%20it%20to%20be%20secretive.%20Even%20with%20the%20new%20digital%20personal%20data%20protection%20act%202023%2C%20all%20the%20fines%20related%20to%20data%20breaches%20go%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20removing%20any%20incentives%20for%20people%20to%20report%20them%20to%20a%20potential%20Data%20Protection%20Board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20number%20of%20these%20cybersecurity%20experts%20are%20now%20being%20hired%20by%20private%20security%20agencies%20to%20provide%20hack%20for%20hire%20services%20across%20the%20globe.%20Stories%20of%20hack%20for%20hire%20companies%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Finvestigates%2Fspecial-report%2Fusa-hackers-litigation%2F%5C%22%3EBellTrox%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Finvestigates%2Fspecial-report%2Fusa-hackers-appin%2F%5C%22%3EAppin%3C%2Fa%3E%20tell%20the%20links%20between%20domestic%20cybersecurity%20companies%20and%20Indian%20security%20establishments%20like%20the%20Intelligence%20Bureau%2C%20RAW%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%2C%20CBI%2C%20ED%2C%20Income%20Tax%20and%20the%20major%20security%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20security%20establishment%20always%20followed%20a%20security%20through%20secrecy%20model%2C%20where%20information%20is%20usually%20hidden%20from%20the%20public.%20CERT-IN%20is%20also%20being%20fit%20into%20that%20model%20where%20no%20information%20is%20shared%20with%20anyone%20outside%20the%20security%20industry.%20With%20CERT-IN%20in%20charge%20of%20responding%20to%20security%20incidents%20related%20to%20spyware%2C%20the%20security%20establishment%20needs%20this%20organisation%20to%20be%20as%20secretive%20as%20it%20can%20get.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20security%20agency%20investigating%20one%20of%20its%20peers%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20very%20unlikely%20to%20get%20any%20major%20updates%20in%20the%20current%20setup.%20It%20would%20be%20wishful%20thinking%20to%20even%20imagine%20a%20scenario%20where%20this%20entire%20apparatus%20actually%20goes%20through%20any%20surveillance%20reforms.%20While%20the%20demand%20from%20the%20opposition%20at%20large%20has%20been%20transparency%20and%20accountability%20of%20these%20intelligence%20agencies%2C%20we%20are%20witnessing%20the%20opposite%20with%20all%20the%20gates%20of%20information%20being%20closed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fskodali%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESrinivas%20Kodali%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20researcher%20on%20digitisation%20and%20a%20hacktivist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700879448000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F05134059%2Fcomputer-1591018_960_720.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fcert-in-goes-exempt-from-rti-amid-apple-investigation-and-finmin-server-breach%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20security%20establishment%20always%20followed%20a%20security%20through%20secrecy%20model.%20CERT-IN%20is%20also%20being%20fit%20into%20that%20model%20where%20no%20information%20is%20shared%20with%20anyone%20outside%20the%20security%20industry.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fcert-in-goes-exempt-from-rti-amid-apple-investigation-and-finmin-server-breach%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kris%20Wu's%20appeal%20in%20rape%20case%20rejected%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700879406000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105486254%2Cimgsize-46196.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fchinese-court-rejects-canadian-pop-