%20Trapped%20Tunnel%20Workers%2C%20But%20Encounter%20Another%20Hurdle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20an%20earlier%20press%20conference%2C%20senior%20officials%20had%20announced%20that%20only%2010-12%20metres%20of%20drilling%20remained%20before%20reaching%20the%20trapped%20construction%20workers%2C%20confirming%20that%20ground-penetrating%20radar%20had%20not%20detected%20any%20significant%20metallic%20obstacles%20within%20the%20next%20five%20metres.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(a%20team%20of%20ground%20penetrating%20experts)%20could%20not%20say%20this%20with%20100%25%20accuracy%20but%20what%20they%20are%20expecting%20is%20that%20there%20is%20no%20continuous%20metal%20object%2C%20like%20girders%2C%20pipes%20and%20metal%20plates%2C%20in%20the%20next%205.4%20metres.%20They%20have%20pointed%20out%20some%20other%20hurdles%2C%20but%20this%20is%20good%20news%2C%26quot%3B%20Uttarakhand%20Secretary%20Neeraj%20Khairwal%2C%20who%20is%20the%20nodal%20officer%20for%20the%20rescue%20operation%2C%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAs%20the%20drilling%20machine%20bores%20its%20way%20forward%2C%20six-metre%20sections%20of%20steel%20pipe%20are%20welded%20together%20and%20pushed%20into%20the%20narrow%20tunnel%20passage.%20Once%20the%20steel%20chute%20is%20in%20place%2C%20rescuers%20will%20utilise%20wheeled%20stretchers%20to%20safely%20evacuate%20the%20workers%20through%20the%20newly%20created%20tunnel.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOn%20Friday%20evening%2C%20rescue%20workers%20said%20that%20the%20drill%20bit%20was%20being%20withdrawn%20through%20the%20passage%20carved%20by%20the%20drilling%20machine.%20The%20two%20setbacks%20encountered%20within%20a%20span%20of%20two%20days%20have%20dealt%20a%20blow%20to%20anxious%20relatives%20camped%20outside%20the%20tunnel%20for%20several%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPrior%20to%20the%20operations%20being%20halted%2C%2046.8%20metres%20of%20the%20800-millimetre-wide%20steel%20pipe%20had%20been%20inserted%20into%20the%20dri