0%5C%22%3EDerek%20Chauvin%2C%20the%20former%20Minneapolis%20police%20officer%20convicted%20of%20murdering%20George%20Floyd%2C%20was%20stabbed%20by%20another%20inmate%20at%20a%20federal%20prison%20in%20Arizona.%20Chauvin%2C%20who%20is%20serving%20a%2021-year%20federal%20sentence%20for%20violating%20Floyd's%20civil%20rights%2C%20was%20seriously%20injured%20in%20the%20attack.%20The%20incident%20occurred%20at%20the%20Federal%20Correctional%20Institution%2C%20Tucson%2C%20a%20medium-security%20prison%20that%20has%20had%20security%20lapses%20and%20staffing%20shortages.%20The%20Bureau%20of%20Prisons%20confirmed%20the%20assault%20and%20stated%20that%20the%20inmate%20who%20attacked%20Chauvin%20has%20been%20taken%20to%20a%20hospital%20for%20treatment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fex-officer-derek-chauvin-convicted-in-george-floyds-killing-stabbed-in-prison%2Farticleshow%2F105486162.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fex-officer-derek-chauvin-convicted-in-george-floyds-killing-stabbed-in-prison%2Famp_articleshow%2F105486162.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fex-officer-derek-chauvin-convicted-in-george-floyds-killing-stabbed-in-prison%2Famp_articleshow%2F105486162.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sex%20Abuse%20Suits%20Filed%20Against%20Several%20Celebrities%20As%20New%20York%20Law%20Expires%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20flurry%20of%20high-profile%20sexual%20abuse%20lawsuits%20were%20filed%20in%20New%20York%20this%20week%20to%20beat%20the%20expiration%20of%20a%20state%20law%20that%20temporarily%20lifted%20the%20statute%20of%20limitations%20on%20civil%20abuse%20and%20harassment%20claims%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20of%20defendants%20includes%20New%20York%20Mayor%20Eric%20Adams%2C%20music%20mogul%20Sean%20%26quot%3BDiddy%26quot%3B%20Combs%2C%20and%20rock%20legend%20Axl%20Rose%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20could%20face%20jury%20trials%20if%20the%20claims%20against%20them%20aren't%20dismissed%20or%20settled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adult%20Survivors%20Act%2C%20passed%20by%20New%20York%20lawmakers%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BMe%20Too%26quot%3B%20movement%2C%20took%20effect%20Nov.%2024%2C%202022%2C%20and%20expired%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Adult%20Survivors%20Act%20has%20enabled%20thousands%20of%20survivors%20to%20pursue%20justice%20that%20was%20previously%20unavailable%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Susan%20Crumiller%2C%20whose%20firm%20has%20handled%20several%20ASA%20cases.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20flood%20of%20last-minute%20cases%20shows%20how%20desperately%20we%20need%20a%20reopened%20window.%20Many%20people%20are%20just%20learning%20about%20the%20Act.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20person%20sued%20under%20the%20law%20-%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20-%20was%20held%20liable%20by%20a%20Manhattan%20jury%20in%20May%20for%20sexually%20abusing%20New%20York%20author%20E.%20Jean%20Carroll%20in%20the%201990s%20and%20ordered%20to%20pay%20%245%20million%20in%20damages%2C%20showing%20how%20the%20statute%20can%20be%20successfully%20used%20in%20court%20even%20when%20the%20claims%20are%20decades%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20that%20early%20win%2C%20most%20cases%20under%20the%20law%20are%20in%20the%20early%20stages.%20Here%20are%20some%20of%20the%20defendants%20in%20suits%20filed%20this%20week%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEric%20Adams%2C%20New%20York%20City%20mayor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%245%20million%20lawsuit%20was%20filed%20on%20November%2022%20by%20a%20woman%20who%20alleges%20she%20was%20assaulted%20by%20the%20Democratic%20politician%20in%201993%20when%20they%20were%20both%20working%20for%20the%20City%20of%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20two-page%20summons%20gives%20a%20bare-bones%20outline%20of%20the%20complaint%2C%20saying%20it%20alleges%20%26quot%3Bsexual%20assault%2C%20battery%20and%20employment%20discrimination.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20claims%20brought%20here%20allege%20intentional%20and%20negligent%20acts%20and%20omissions%20for%20physical%2C%20psychological%2C%20and%20other%20injuries%20suffered%20as%20a%20result%20of%20conduct%20that%20would%20constitute%20sexual%20offenses%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdams%20denied%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20mayor%20does%20not%20know%20who%20this%20person%20is.%20If%20they%20ever%20met%2C%20he%20doesn't%20recall%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Adams.%20%26quot%3BBut%20he%20would%20never%20do%20anything%20to%20physically%20harm%20another%20person%20and%20vigorously%20denies%20any%20such%20claim.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAndrew%20Cuomo%2C%20former%20New%20York%20governor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20suit%20filed%20Nov.%2022%20by%20Cuomo's%20former%20executive%20assistant%2C%20Brittany%20Commisso%2C%20accuses%20the%20former%20governor%20of%20groping%20her%20breast%20and%20buttocks.%20Commisso%20claims%20that%20she%20suffered%20%26quot%3Bsubstantial%20personal%20injuries%20and%20economic%20loss%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20alleged%20abuse%2C%20as%20well%20as%20gender%20discrimination%20and%20retaliation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20continuous%20sexual%20harassment%20by%20defendant%20Cuomo%20included%20unwelcome%20sexual%20advances%2C%20sexualized%20comments%20about%20appearance%20and%20personal%20matters%2C%20relations%2C%20their%20dating%2C%20their%20sex%20life%2C%20and%20her%20marriage%2C%20assignment%20of%20humiliating%20and%20demeaning%20tasks%2C%20hugs%2C%20kisses%2C%20sexual%20touching%20of%20the%20buttocks%2C%20and%20forcible%20touching%20of%20the%20breast%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommisso%2C%20formerly%20identified%20only%20as%20%26quot%3Bexecutive%20assistant%20%231%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20damning%20report%20on%20Cuomo's%20conduct%20by%20the%20state%20attorney%20general%2C%20went%20public%20with%20her%20allegations%20more%20than%20two%20years%20ago%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20CBS%20News%20and%20the%20Albany%20Times%20Union.%20Cuomo%20has%20strenuously%20denied%20her%20allegations%2C%20as%20well%20as%20similar%20claims%20made%20by%20other%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BMs.%20Commisso's%20claims%20are%20provably%20false%2C%20which%20is%20why%20the%20Albany%20District%20Attorney%20dismissed%20the%20case%20two%20years%20ago%20after%20a%20thorough%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokeswoman%20for%20Cuomo%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BMs.%20Commisso's%20transparent%20attempt%20at%20a%20cash%20grab%20will%20fail.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESean%20%26quot%3BDiddy%26quot%3B%20Combs%2C%20music%20mogul%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20suit%20filed%20on%20Thanksgiving%20Day%20alleges%20Combs%20drugged%20and%20raped%20a%20Syracuse%20University%20student%20during%20a%20date%20in%201991.%20The%20complaint%20by%20Joi%20Dickerson-Neal%20claims%20she%20suffered%20%26quot%3Bsubstantial%20and%20lifetime%20injuries%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20assault%2C%20which%20she%20alleges%20was%20videotaped%20by%20Combs%20and%20shown%20to%20other%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20sexual%20assault%20and%20public%20exposure%20of%20it%2C%20caused%20her%20to%20suffer%20overwhelming%20feelings%20of%20humiliation%2C%20embarrassment%2C%20violation%2C%20and%20constant%20apprehension%20about%20who%20all%20viewed%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDickerson-Neal%20claims%20the%20alleged%20assault%20sent%20her%20life%20into%20a%20tailspin%2C%20forcing%20her%20to%20seek%20medical%20help%20for%20depression%20and%20impeding%20her%20ability%20to%20finish%20college%20as%20Combs%20rose%20to%20fame%20and%20fortune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20lawsuit%20against%20Combs%20under%20the%20Adult%20Survivors%20Act%20was%20filed%20the%20same%20day%20by%20an%20anonymous%20plaintiff.%20The%20court%20docket%20says%20the%20complaint%20was%20%26quot%3Breturned%20for%20correction%26quot%3B%20and%20isn't%20yet%20available.%20The%20new%20complaints%20were%20filed%20about%20a%20week%20after%20Combs%20settled%20similar%20claims%20by%20a%20former%20girlfriend%2C%20Casandra%20Ventura.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Combs%20denied%20the%20allegations%2C%20describing%20the%20Dickerson-Neal%20suit%20as%20%26quot%3Ban%20example%20of%20how%20a%20well-intentioned%20law%20can%20be%20turned%20on%20its%20head.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3B32-year-old%20story%20is%20made%20up%20and%20not%20credible%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BMr.%20Combs%20never%20assaulted%20her%2C%20and%20she%20implicates%20companies%20that%20did%20not%20exist.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20Jane%20Doe%20allegations%20are%20%26quot%3Bare%20fabricated%20claims%20falsely%20alleging%20misconduct%20from%20over%2030%20years%20ago%20and%20filed%20at%20the%20last%20minute%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAxl%20Rose%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20suit%20filed%20on%20November%2022%20by%20California%20actress%20and%20model%20Sheila%20Kennedy%20alleges%20she%20was%20assaulted%20by%20Rose%20in%201989%2C%20when%20the%20Guns%20N'%20Roses%20singer%20%26quot%3Bwas%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20his%20commercial%20success.%26quot%3B%20According%20to%20the%20complaint%2C%20Rose%20%26quot%3Bused%20his%20fame%2C%20status%2C%20and%20power%20as%20a%20celebrity%20and%20performer%20in%20the%20music%20industry%20to%20gain%20access%20to%20manipulate%2C%20control%2C%20and%20violently%20sexually%20assault%20Kennedy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20outlines%20previous%20allegations%20of%20wrongdoing%20against%20Rose%20and%20c