20performance%20in%20Patna%2C%20India%20found%20itself%20in%20the%20throes%20of%20a%20catastrophic%20second%20wave%20of%20Covid-19%20infections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20indifference%20towards%20the%20pandemic%20had%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20fatally%20misplaced.%20A%20devastating%20deluge%20of%20Covid-19%20cases%20overwhelmed%20the%20country%20in%20the%20months%20of%20April%20and%20May%202021%2C%20leaving%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20hospitals%20and%20cemeteries%20flooded.%20Patients%20found%20no%20place%20to%20go%2C%20nor%20did%20the%20dead.%20People%20were%20falling%20dead%20on%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20streets%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20everything%2C%20from%20hospital%20beds%20to%20oxygen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Kamal%2C%20all%20this%20had%20meant%20a%20slew%20of%20show%20cancellations%20and%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20fresh%20financial%20crisis.%3Cbr%3E%5CnEver%20since%20the%20pandemic%20began%20in%202020%2C%20Kamal%E2%80%99s%20income%20had%20fluctuated%20wildly.%20The%20money%20from%20live%20shows%E2%80%94which%20was%20the%20bulk%20of%20his%20income%E2%80%94had%20come%20down%20to%20naught.%20After%20the%20first%20wave%20of%20cases%20ebbed%2C%20live%20shows%20had%20slowly%20started%20taking%20off.%20The%20show%20in%20Patna%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20ones%20that%20Kamal%20had%20performed%20at%20since%20the%20pandemic.%20The%20second%20wave%20seemed%20devastating%2C%20and%20Kamal%20feared%20that%20shows%20might%20not%20resume%20that%20year%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThankfully%20for%20Kamal%20and%20his%20ilk%2C%20the%20second%20wave%20of%20infections%20peaked%20in%20May%20and%20by%20July%2C%20cases%20had%20dipped%20substantially%2C%20and%20kavi%20sammelans%20had%20started%20taking%20place.%20I%20told%20Kamal%20that%20I%20was%20keen%20to%20attend%20some%20more%20sammelans%20with%20him%2C%20to%20see%20him%20perform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20getting%20calls%20to%20perform%20at%20some%20sammelans%2C%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%98Lekin%20kuch%20mazza%20nahi%20lag%20raha.%E2%80%99%20It%20didn%E2%80%99t%20sound%20any%20fun%2C%20he%20would%20say%2C%20to%20justify%20why%20those%20calls%20weren%E2%80%99t%20materializing%20into%20performances.%20This%2C%20I%20later%20deciphered%2C%20meant%20that%20either%20the%20money%20offered%20was%20paltry%20or%20the%20show%20was%20too%20local%20for%20him%20to%20be%20associated%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20seemed%20perplexing%2C%20because%20Kamal%20needed%20the%20money.%20His%20expenses%20were%20piling%20up.%20He%20had%20wanted%20to%20buy%20a%20new%20motorcycle%20for%20home%20so%20that%20his%20father%20did%20not%20have%20to%20depend%20on%20his%20brothers%20to%20be%20driven%20around.%20Kamal%20had%20his%20own%20expenses%E2%80%94from%20rent%20to%20the%20living%20costs%20that%20came%20with%20staying%20in%20a%20posh%20locality%20in%20Greater%20Noida%2C%20even%20if%20he%20shared%20it%20with%20two%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20for%20Kamal%2C%20saying%20no%20was%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20320px)%2085vw%2C%20320px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24223510%2FH-Hop-cover.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22320%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24223510%2FH-Hop-cover.jpg%20780w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24223510%2FH-Hop-cover-195x300.jpg%20195w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24223510%2FH-Hop-cover-666x1024.jpg%20666w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686298%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22492%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKunal%20Purohit%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EH-Pop%3A%20The%20Secretive%20World%20of%20Hindutva%20Pop%20Stars%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3EHarperCollins%2C%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamal%20grew%20up%20in%20Gosaiganj%2C%20a%20small%20town%20with%20a%20population%20of%20less%20than%2010%2C000%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Lucknow%2C%20a%20forty-minute%20drive%20from%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20city%20of%20nawabs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20there%20that%20he%20had%20witnessed%20his%20life%E2%80%99s%20first-ever%20poetry%20recital%2C%20a%20kavya%20goshti.%20The%20goshti%20was%20mostly%20a%20meeting%20of%20local%20poets%2C%20where%20they%20would%20recite%20their%20own%20material%20and%20discuss%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20work.%20Kamal%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20Ashok%20Varma%2C%20a%20connoisseur%20of%20poetry%2C%20knew%20all%20the%20local%20poets%20closely%20and%20attended%20these%20goshtis%20religiously.%20Slowly%2C%20Kamal%20started%20tagging%20along.%20In%20these%20goshtis%2C%20one%20of%20the%20poets%20who%20immediately%20stood%20out%20for%20Kamal%20was%20a%20local%20schoolteacher%20poet%20named%20Rameshwar%20Prasad%20Dwivedi%20Pralayankar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPralayankar%20is%20a%20nationalist%20poet%2C%20and%20much%20like%20Kamal%2C%20his%20poems%20deal%20with%20social%20and%20political%20matters.%20Back%20then%2C%20he%20would%20perform%20at%20locally%20organized%20kavya%20goshtis%20and%20Kamal%2C%20still%20in%20school%2C%20would%20attend%20these%20programmes%20and%20be%20blown%20away%20by%20Pralayankar%E2%80%99s%20talent%2C%20his%20commitment%20to%20the%20Hindu%20cause%20as%20well%20as%20his%20mastery%20over%20the%20Hindi%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20Kamal%20grew%20to%20emulate%20his%20guru%2C%20one%20thing%20struck%20him%20as%20odd%20about%20Pralayankar%E2%80%94for%20all%20his%20talent%2C%20Pralayankar%20had%20won%20barely%20any%20recognition%20outside%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98He%20has%20never%20been%20very%20career-minded%20about%20his%20poetry.%20Maybe%20because%20of%20his%20full-time%20job%20as%20a%20teacher%2C%20he%20never%20wanted%20to%20push%20his%20boundaries%2C%E2%80%99%20Kamal%20told%20me.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20he%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20perform%20at%20bigger%20events%20that%20involved%20travelling.%20Be%20it%20Lucknow%20or%20Delhi%2C%20Pralayankar%20would%20end%20up%20saying%20no%20to%20many%20prestigious%20events%20because%20he%20could%20not%20afford%20to%20be%20gone%20from%20work%20for%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20way%20to%20make%20up%20for%20this%2C%20Pralayankar%20would%20accept%20all%20invitations%20he%20got%20around%20Gosaiganj%2C%20travelling%20across%20districts%2C%20even%20to%20smaller%2C%20local%20kavi%20sammelans%2C%20without%20regard%20for%20money%20or%20fame.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Woh%20toh%20kahin%20bhi%20nikal%20jaate%20the%2C%20apne%20scooter%20par.%E2%80%99%20He%20would%20readily%20set%20off%20on%20his%20scooter%20for%20any%20kind%20of%20event.%3Cbr%3E%5CnKamal%20used%20to%20be%20uncomfortable%20watching%20his%20guru%20do%20this.%20For%20him%2C%20readily%20going%20to%20smaller%20events%2C%20without%20any%20prestige%20or%20money%20meant%20that%20people%20took%20your%20talent%20and%20skills%20for%20granted.%20It%20also%20meant%20that%20you%20would%20get%20comfortable%20with%20whatever%20came%20your%20way%2C%20without%20having%20the%20hunger%20for%20more%E2%80%94bigger%20stages%2C%20more%20crowds%2C%20more%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Kamal%2C%20that%20was%20unacceptable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20where%20he%20had%20to%20make%20his%20break%20with%20his%20guru.%20Kamal%20was%20ambitious%20and%20had%20staked%20it%20all%20in%20the%20world%20of%20poetry.%20Money%20and%20fame%20were%20important.%20Each%20time%20he%20would%20get%20offered%20local%20gigs%2C%20with%20little%20prospect%20of%20decent%20money%20or%20exposure%2C%20Kamal%20would%20think%20of%20his%20first%20guru%20and%20inevitably%20refuse%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%20October%202021%2C%20around%20the%20nine-day%20festival%20of%20Navratri%E2%80%94at%20the%20end%20of%20which%20Lord%20Ram%20slays%20Ravana%20and%20marks%20the%20end%20of%20the%20war%20in%20the%20Ramayana%E2%80%94that%20things%20finally%20started%20to%20pick%20up%20for%20Kamal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20first%20shows%20that%20he%20got%20was%20a%20kavi%20sammelan%20in%20Rasoolabad%2C%20a%20small%20town%20in%20Kanpur%20district%2C%20slightly%20over%20ninety%20minutes%20away%20from%20Kanpur%20city.%20The%20organizers%20of%20the%20event%20were%20the%20local%20committee%20that%20primarily%20organized%20the%20Ramlila%2C%20a%20dramatic%20re-enactment%20of%20the%20Ramcharitamanas%20over%20the%20nine%20days%20festival.%20The%20sammelan%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20the%20big%20showstopper%20and%20was%20slated%20to%20happen%20a%20day%20after%20Dussehra%2C%20on%2016%20October%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamal%20said%20he%20would%20be%20free%20to%20perform%20%E2%80%98whatever%20he%20wanted%E2%80%99%20at%20this%20event%2C%20which%20meant%20that%20there%20was%20no%20one%20to%20tame%20his%20political%20poetry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccompanying%20him%20to%20the%20sammelan%20was%20a%20mouth-watering%20prospect%20for%20me.%20Not%20just%20because%20of%20the%20event%20itself%20but%20the%20broader%20political%20context%20around%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20temperature%20across%20the%20country%2C%20but%20especially%20in%20UP%2C%20was%20soaring.%20The%20state%20was%20going%20to%20go%20to%20polls%20in%20four%20months%2C%20elections%20that%20would%20decide%20the%20fate%20of%20its%20Hindu%20nationalist%20chief%20minister%20and%20Hindutva%20icon%2C%20Adityanath.%20The%20elections%20would%20also%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20referendum%20on%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20governance%20since%20the%20party%20had%20dominated%20UP%E2%80%99s%20politics%20since%202014%20when%20he%20came%20to%20power.%20The%20state%20sent%20eighty%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20543%20MPs%20to%20the%20Parliament.%20It%20was%20important%20for%20Modi%20to%20continue%20retaining%20a%20solid%20grip%20on%20it.%20But%20things%20had%20seemed%20to%20be%20slipping%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protest%20by%20farmers%2C%20against%20the%20three%20agrarian%20laws%20enacted%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20had%20been%20heating%20up.%20Just%20days%20before%2C%20three%20cars%2C%20containing%20BJP%20leaders%20and%20workers%2C%20including%20Ashish%20Mishra%2C%20the%20son%20of%20the%20Union%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Home%20Ajay%20Mishra%20Teni%2C%20ran%20over%20a%20group%20of%20protesting%20farmers%20in%20UP%E2%80%99s%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20district.%20Eight%20people%2C%20including%20four%20farmers%2C%20one%20journalist%2C%20two%20BJP%20workers%20in%20the%20cars%20and%20Mishra%E2%80%99s%20driver%2C%20were%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20killings%20had%20caused%20outrage%20across%20the%20nation.%20Protests%20broke%20out%2C%20with%20farmer%20groups%20and%20Opposition%20parties%20demanding%20that%20Mishra%20be%20arrested%20and%20his%20father%20Teni%20be%20sacked%20from%20his%20post%20to%20enable%20a%20fair%20investigation.%20Opposition%20parties%20made%20a%20beeline%20for%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%2C%20but%20they%20were%20stopped%20from%20entering%20the%20district.%20The%20Congress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20was%20arrested%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20Chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20was%20put%20under%20house%20arrest%2C%20while%20other%20Opposition%20figures%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20leave%20the%20Lucknow%20airport.%20Five%20days%20later%2C%20Mishra%20was%20finally%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20had%20shaken%20the%20nation%2C%20with%20viral%20videos%20showing%20the%20car%20ramming%20into%20the%20protesting%20farmers%20being%20played%20on%20loop%20on%20social%20media%20and%20across%20news%20channels.%20The%20BJP%20tried%20hard%20to%20deflect%20blame.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20crisis%20like%20this%20could%20hurt%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20chances%2C%20and%20I%20had%20little%20doubt%20that%20the%20party%20would%20do%20all%20it%20takes%20to%20wrest%20the%20narrative%20in%20its%20favour.%20In%20this%2C%20Kamal%20and%20his%20ilk%E2%80%94poets%20and%20influencers%E2%80%94would%20be%20crucial%20to%20plant%20an%20alternativ