ss%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Tawang%20Festival%2C%20in%20November%202023.%20Photo%3A%20Sattyakee%20D%E2%80%99com%20Bhuyan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20famous%20Aji-Lhamu%20dance%2C%20Arpuchham%20(war%20dance)%20by%20various%20villages%2C%20yak%20dance%2C%20lion%20dance%2C%20Ngagchham%20(the%20tantric%20dance)%2C%20Phan%20Chham%20(the%20flag%20dance)%20and%20Yapchenapayumchhen%20Ama%20dance%2C%20were%20performed%2C%20along%20with%20various%20other%20traditional%20dances%20and%20rituals.%20The%20monastic%20dances%20and%20street%20performances%20were%20particularly%20delightful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20performances%20also%20provide%20insights%20into%20the%20Monpa%20way%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24164419%2Fimage-1535.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24164419%2Fimage-1535.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24164419%2Fimage-1535-300x166.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24164419%2Fimage-1535-1024x565.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686251%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22662%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20street%20carnival%20drew%20thousands%20of%20tourists%2C%20apart%20from%20local%20residents%2C%20who%20reveled%20in%20the%20rich%20cultural%20tapestry%20on%20display.%20Photo%3A%20Sattyakee%20D%E2%80%99com%20Bhuyan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Guwahati-based%20pulmonologist%2C%20Dr.%20Moitreyee%20Kalita%2C%20the%20Tawang%20Festival%20is%20all%20about%20rich%20traditions.%20%E2%80%9CI%20grew%20up%20learning%20Bharatanatyam%20and%20Hindustani%20Classical%20music%2C%20and%20I%20am%20here%20with%20my%20eight-year-old%20daughter%2C%20Tuhi.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20the%20company%20of%20endearing%20friends%20and%20the%20cultural%20melee%20of%20colours%20and%20music%2C%20the%20festival%20infused%20in%20me%20a%20dream-like%20quality%20.%20I%20can%20never%20get%20enough%20of%20this%20place%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20like%20a%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20embrace.%20It%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20simple%20yet%20breathtakingly%20gorgeous%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20the%20yak%20dance%20in%20itself%20is%20a%20vibrant%20and%20colourful%20performance%20that%20celebrates%20the%20significance%20of%20yaks%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20Monpa%20people.%20Yaks%20are%20revered%20for%20their%20utility%20in%20this%20region%20as%20they%20are%20used%20for%20transportation%2C%20milk%2C%20and%20wool.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20performers%20dress%20up%20in%20elaborate%20costumes%2C%20resembling%20yaks%2C%20complete%20with%20masks%20and%20fur.%20They%20mimic%20the%20movements%20and%20behaviour%20of%20yaks%2C%20such%20as%20engaging%20in%20activities%20like%20grazing%20and%20playful%20interactions.%20The%20dance%20is%20often%20accompanied%20by%20traditional%20music%20and%20songs%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20cultural%20richness%20of%20the%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Longnit%20Terang%2C%20a%20senior%20Assam%20Police%20Service%20Officer%2C%20with%20a%20deep%20passion%20for%20photography%2C%20it%20was%20his%20first%20visit%20to%20Tawang%20for%20the%20majestic%20festival.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20vibrant%20colours%2C%20the%20beauty%2C%20and%20the%20serenity%20of%20the%20land%20are%20beyond%20words%20to%20describe.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20kind%20of%20divinity%20in%20the%20air%20of%20Tawang%20and%20to%20capture%20the%20cultural%20parade%20through%20my%20lens%20and%20to%20carry%20the%20warmth%20of%20Tawang%20back%20home%20is%20an%20experience%20that%20I%E2%80%99ll%20cherish%20forever%20and%20it%20does%20feel%20surreal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20within%20the%20ancient%20tapestry%20of%20Tibetan%20traditions%2C%20a%20dance%20unfolds%20that%20whispers%20tales%20of%20mythical%20grace%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Snow%20Lion%20Dance.%20Cloaked%20in%20the%20ethereal%20white%20of%20pristine%20snow%2C%20performers%20embody%20these%20legendary%20creatures%2C%20symbols%20of%20power%2C%20strength%2C%20and%20unyielding%20fearlessness%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Tibetan%20lore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20joy%20cascades%20down%20the%20valleys%20and%20jubilation%20graces%20the%20air%2C%20the%20Snow%20Lion%20Dance%20takes%20center%20stage.%20Its%20choreography%2C%20a%20dance%20of%20delicate%20rhythms%2C%20mirrors%20the%20heartbeat%20of%20a%20culture%20rich%20in%20history.%20Adorned%20in%20costumes%20that%20mirror%20the%20majestic%20snow%20lions%2C%20resplendent%20in%20white%20with%20accents%20of%20vibrant%20hues%2C%20the%20dancers%20become%20living%20embodiments%20of%20folklore.%20With%20each%20graceful%20sway%2C%20they%20carry%20the%20weight%20of%20tradition%2C%20a%20symbolic%20odyssey%20through%20the%20annals%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20independent%20researcher%20working%20on%20indigenous%20cultures%20and%20traditions%20of%20her%20land%2C%20this%20is%20Girbani%E2%80%99s%20third%20visit%20to%20the%20Tawang%20Festival.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20mountains%20that%20echo%20happiness%2C%20this%20festival%20is%20a%20tale%20where%20the%20winds%20chant%20a%20zillion%20dreams%2C%20where%20colours%20splatter%20hope%20and%20where%20hearts%20beam%20with%20joy.%20Befittingly%20called%20the%20Festival%20of%20Dreams%2C%20it%20is%20as%20gorgeous%20as%20the%20land.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20further%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20visit%20to%20Tawang%20for%20me%20has%20always%20been%20very%20enriching%20and%20the%20simplicity%20of%20the%20people%2C%20its%20food%2C%20the%20textiles%2C%20the%20aroma%20of%20the%20land%20and%20its%20culture%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98Tashi%20Delek%E2%80%99%20greetings%20with%20a%20bright%20warm%20smile%20now%20and%20then%20is%20a%20reminder%20of%20the%20warmth%20in%20the%20hearts%20of%20every%20Monpa.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20hospitality%20we%20received%20as%20tourists%20was%20overwhelming%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Priyanka%20Gogoi%2C%20an%20Avid%20illustrator%2C%20based%20out%20of%20Dubai.%20She%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20surprise%20to%20see%20special%20seating%20arrangements%20made%20for%20tourists%20to%20witness%20the%20cultural%20parade%2C%20covered%20seats%20at%20the%20evening%20cultural%20programme%20and%20the%20likes%3B%20kudos%20to%20the%20tourism%20department%20for%20showering%20such%20hospitality!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24170158%2Fimage-1536.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24170158%2Fimage-1536.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24170158%2Fimage-1536-300x133.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24170158%2Fimage-1536-1024x455.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686253%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22533%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Tawang%20Festival%2C%20in%20November%202023.%20Photo%3A%20Sattyakee%20D%E2%80%99com%20Bhuyan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20dance%20form%20that%20drew%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20attention%20was%20the%20Keng%20Cham.%20It%20is%20often%20associated%20with%20Buddhist%20rituals%20and%20is%20performed%20to%20invoke%20blessings%2C%20ward%20off%20evil%20spirits%2C%20and%20celebrate%20various%20cultural%20events%20within%20the%20Monpa%20community.%20It%20is%20performed%20by%20bare%20bodied%20dancers%20in%20a%20pair%20of%20shorts%20and%20a%20skeleton-face%20mask.%20This%20dance%20symbolises%20defeat%20of%20evils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20spirit%20of%20cultural%20unity%20and%20diversity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20all%20the%20three%20days%2C%20as%20the%20sun%20dipped%20below%20the%20horizon%2C%20the%20festivities%20transitioned%20to%20the%20grand%20Mentsem-Tse%20Tawang%20festival%20ground.%20The%20monks%20of%20the%20Tawang%20Monastery%20set%20the%20tone%20with%20the%20Mangalacharan%2C%20despite%20the%20bone-chilling%20cold%20weather%20on%20the%20very%20first%20day.%20The%20chief%20minister%20officially%20inaugurated%20the%20festival%20from%20the%20festival%20stage%2C%20greeted%20by%20a%20packed%20assemblage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20spirit%20of%20festivals%20fosters%20cultural%20unity%20and%20strengthens%20the%20idea%20of%20diversity%2C%20and%20moreover%2C%20we%20are%20proud%20of%20our%20state%2C%20which%20is%20a%20biodiversity%20hotspot%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20clad%20in%20his%20traditional%20black%20Khanjar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeign%20dignitaries%2C%20domestic%20tourists%2C%20and%20artists%20from%20Bhutan%20and%20various%20other%20Indian%20states%20added%20to%20the%20festive%20spirit%2C%20making%20the%20occasion%20truly%20remarkable.%20Among%20the%20artists%20invited%20to%20the%20festival%20were%20Bhutanese%20alternative%20rock%20Band%2C%20%E2%80%98Misty%20Terrace%2C%E2%80%99%20featuring%20frontman%20Tandin%20Wangchuk%3B%20singers%20Rito%20Riba%2C%20Ladakhi%20Faisal%20Ashnoor%2C%20and%20Nepali%20singer%20Anjhila%20Regmi%3B%20Sa%20Re%20Ga%20Ma%20Pa%20Li%E2%80%99l%20Champs%20winner%20Jetshen%20Dohna%3B%20and%20singer%20Monali%20Thakur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20record%2C%20the%20Tawang%20Festival%20is%20a%20relatively%20recent%20addition%20to%20the%20cultural%20calendar%20of%20Arunachal%20Pradesh.%20It%20was%20first%20organised%20in%202012%20by%20the%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20Tourism%20Department%2C%20with%20the%20primary%20goal%20of%20promoting%20tourism%20in%20the%20region%20and%20safeguarding%20the%20indigenous%20culture%20of%20the%20Monpa%20tribe.%20Since%20its%20inception%2C%20the%20festival%20has%20gained%20prominence%2C%20drawing%20visitors%20from%20distant%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20consider%20this%20festival%20as%20a%20means%20to%20showcase%20our%20age-old%20traditions%20and%20heritage%20to%20the%20world.%20We%20make%20special%20arrangements%20for%20the%20tourists%20who%20can%20benefit%20from%20this%20festival.%20They%20can%20witness%20and%20immerse%20themselves%20in%20the%20rich%20cultural%20tapestry%20of%20our%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20artist%20and%20festival%20curator%20Ranjan%20Engti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNestled%20amidst%20the%20picturesque%20landscapes%20of%20the%20northeastern%20Indian%20state%20of%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Tawang%20is%20renowned%20not%20only%20for%20its%20breathtaking%20beauty%20but%20also%20for%20its%20profound%20cultural%20heritage%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20one%20could%20engage%20in%20gluttony%20amidst%20the%20array%20of%20stalls%20with%20delectable%20dishes%20at%20the%20festival%20ground%2C%20such%20as%20Zan%20(rice%20porridge)%2C%20Thupkas%2C%20a%20noodle%20soup%20mixed%20with%20minced%20meat%2C%20and%20spices%2C%20juicy%20momos%2C%20and%20others%20.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20fond%20of%20the%20Dheb-Thukpa%2C%20which%20is%20cooked%20with%20rice%20and%20the%20Thukpa%20made%20of%20maize%2C%20meat%2C%20and%20beans%2C%20which%20we%20traditionally%20call%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CAshum%20Thukpa%E2%80%9D%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20yummy%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Tenzin%2C%20a%20local%20farmer%2C%20with%20a%20gleam%20in%20his%20eyes%20at%20the%20festival%20ground.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Monali%20Thakur%20belted%20out%20her%20hits%20like%20%E2%80%98Sawaar%20Loon%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Moh%20Moh%20Ke%20Dhaage%E2%80%99%20and%20others%20on%20the%20concluding%20day%20of%20the%20festival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESattyakee%20D%E2%80%99com%20Bhuyan%20is%20founder%20director%20of%20the%20D%E2%80%99Passion%20Collective.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700875855000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24172211%2Fimage-1537.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Ftawang-festival-a-cultural-extravaganza-amidst-breathtaking-landscape-and-vibrant-performances%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Tawang%20Festival%20was%20first%20organised%20in%202012%20by%20the%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20Tourism%20Department%2C%20with%20the%20primary%20goal%20of%20promoting%20tourism%20in%20the%20region.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20festival%20has%20gained%20prominence%2C%20drawing%20visitors%20from%20distant%20places.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Ftawang-festival-a-cultural-extravaganza-amidst-breathtaking-landscape-and-vibrant-performances%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Warren%20Buffett%20exits%20Paytm%2C%20sells%202.5%25%20stake%20for%201%2C371cr%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700875498000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105485869%2Cimgsize-152958.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fbuffett-exits-paytm-sells-2-5-stake-for-1371-crore%2Farticleshow%2F105485698.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Agencies%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fbuffett-exits-paytm-sells-2-5-stake-for-1371-crore%2Farticleshow%2F105485698.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hall%20%26amp%3B%20Oates%E2%80%99%20Restraining%20Order%20Mystery%20Solved%3A%20Daryl%20Hall%20Wants%20to%20Block%20John%20Oates%20From%20Selling%2