%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAndrew%20Cuomo's%20former%20executive%20assistant%20is%20suing%20him%20for%20sexual%20harassment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20former%20New%20York%20governor%20faces%20allegations%20of%20forcible%20touching%20and%20unwelcome%20sexual%20advances.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECuomo's%20attorney%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20lawsuit%20is%20a%C2%A0%26quot%3Bcash%20grab%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20allegations%20are%20false.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20former%20executive%20assistant%20to%20New%20York%20Gov.%20Andrew%20Cuomo%2C%20who%20accused%20him%20of%20groping%20her%20in%20late%202020%2C%20is%20suing%20the%20former%20governor%20under%20New%20York's%20Adult%20Survivors%20Act.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EBrittany%20Commisso%20claims%20in%20court%20papers%20that%20Cuomo's%20%26quot%3Bcontinuous%20sexual%20harassment%26quot%3B%20included%20%26quot%3Bunwelcome%20sexual%20advances%2C%20sexualized%20comments%20about%20appearance%20and%20personal%20matters%2C%20relations%2C%20their%20dating%2C%20their%20sex%20life%2C%20and%20her%20marriage%2C%20assignment%20of%20humiliating%20and%20demeaning%20tasks%2C%20hugs%2C%20kisses%2C%20sexual%20touching%20of%20the%20buttocks%2C%20and%20forcible%20touching%20of%20the%20breast%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20three-page%20summons%20filed%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20document%20said%20Cuomo's%20behavior%20created%20a%20%26quot%3Bpervasive%20hostile%20work%20environment%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20Commisso%20suffered%20%26quot%3Bserious%20physical%2C%20emotional%2C%20and%20psychological%20pain%2C%20suffering%20and%20injuries%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECommisso's%20filing%20came%20just%20days%20before%20New%20York's%20Adult%20Survivors%20Act%20expired.%20The%20law%20provided%20a%20one-year%20window%20for%20adults%20to%20file%20civil%20lawsuits%20related%20to%20sexual%20abuse%20allegations%20that%20would%20otherwise%20have%20been%20past%20the%20statute%20of%20limitations.%20A%20number%20of%20high-profile%20men%