%20being%20contested%20by%201%2C862%20candidates%20and%20the%20total%20number%20of%20voters%20is%205.25%20crore.%20Of%20these%2C%201.71%20crore%20voters%20are%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2018%20and%2030%2C%20and%2022.61%20lakh%20are%20new%20voters%20from%20the%2018-19%20age%20group.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20hoping%20that%20the%20magic%20of%20Ashok%20Gehlot%2C%20who%20is%20known%20as%20%3Cem%3E'jadugar'%3C%2Fem%3E%20(magician)%2C%20its%20seven%20guarantees%20and%20welfare%20measures%20like%20the%20country's%20first%20law%20for%20gig%20workers%20will%20get%20it%20re-elected%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EVoters%20in%20Rajasthan%20have%20not%20given%20any%20government%20a%20second%20term%20since%201993%20and%20the%20BJP%20is%20banking%20on%20this%20as%20well%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20popularity%20to%20return%20to%20power.%20Former%20chief%20minister%20Vasundhara%20Raje%2C%20who%20is%20arguably%20the%20party's%20most%20popular%20leader%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20has%20not%20been%20declared%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20face.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20been%20attacking%20the%20Congress%20on%20issues%20like%20crime%20against%20women%2C%20corruption%20and%20the%20alleged%20paper%20leak%20scams.%20One%20of%20the%20key%20planks%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20used%20against%20Mr%20Gehlot%20is%20the%20'Red%20Diary'%20which%20is%20said%20to%20detail%20irregularities%20committed%20by%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20was%20waved%20in%20the%20Assembly%20by%20sacked%20minister%20Rajendra%20Gudha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20opposition%20party%20is%20also%20hoping%20that%20the%20feud%20between%20Mr%20Gehlot%20and%20his%20former%20deputy%20Sachin%20Pilot%20will%20work%20in%20its%20favour.%20The%20differences%2C%20which%20had%20come%20to%20a%20head%20in%202020%20and%20flared%20up%20earlier%20this%20year%20as%20well%2C%20have%20been%20played%20down%20by%20both%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20Mr%20Pilot%20in%20recent%20weeks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESachin%20Pilot%20also%20issued%20an%20appeal%20to%20vote%20for%20Congress%20candidates%20on%20Friday%2C%20which%20was%20shared%20by%20Ashok%20Gehlot%2C%20in%20a%20gesture%20that%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20sign%20of%20unity%20within%20the%20Congress.%20Mr%20Gehlot%20had%20shared%20the%20video%20on%20X%20and%20called%20Mr%20Pilot%20a%20young%20leader.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESeven%20MPs%2C%20including%20Rajyavardhan%20Rathore%2C%20Diya%20Kumari%20and%20Kirodi%20Lal%20Meena%2C%20have%20been%20fielded%20by%20the%20BJP%20for%20the%20Assembly%20elections.%20Some%20of%20the%20MPs%20-%20all%20of%20whom%20were%20named%20in%20the%20first%20list%20-%20are%20contesting%20seats%20which%20could%20have%20otherwise%20gone%20to%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20loyalists.%20The%20subsequent%20lists%20had%20several%20of%20her%20supporters%20named%20as%20candidates%20and%20were%20seen%20as%20the%20party's%20way%20of%20placating%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOver%201%20lakh%20security%20personnel%20have%20been%20deployed%20to%20ensure%20peaceful%20voting%20in%20the%20single-phase%20election.%20Counting%20of%20votes%20will%20take%20place%20on%20December%203.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700871480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fucfgqjl8_pm-modi-ashok-gehlot-ani-650_650x400_27_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajasthan-elections-rajasthan-elections-live-updates-its-ashok-gehlot-vs-narendra-modi-as-rajasthan-votes-today-10-points-4604187%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rajasthan%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20of%20the%20Congress%20is%20seeking%20a%20second%20term%20in%20a%20state%20known%20for%20its%20revolving-door%20policy%20even%20as%20the%20BJP%20banks%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20popularity%20to%20get%20a%20majority.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajasthan-electi