.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20soldiers%20have%20been%20given%20strict%20instructions%20on%20how%20to%20care%20for%20the%20child%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-hamas-hostages-released-gaza-2023-11%5C%22%3Ehostages%20released%20by%20Hamas%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Friday%20after%20seven%20weeks%20of%20captivity.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jpost.com%2Fisrael-news%2Fdefense-news%2Farticle-774562%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJersulaem%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Israeli%20soldiers%20were%20told%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20children%20feel%20safe%20while%20staying%20away%20from%20questions%20like%20the%20whereabouts%20of%20their%20parents%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20may%20not%20have%20survived%20the%20October%207%20attack%20that%20kicked%20off%20the%20MidEast%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20child%20hostages%20released%20are%20Aviv%20Katz%20Asher%2C%202%3B%20Raz%20Katz%20Asher%2C%204%3B%20Emelia%20Aloni%2C%205%3B%20and%20Ohad%20Munder%2C%209%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister's%20office.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUpon%20meeting%20child%20hostages%2C%20soldiers%20are%20trained%20to%20say%3A%20%26quot%3BHello%2C%20my%20name%20is...%20I%20am%20a%20soldier%20in%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%2C%20and%20I%20am%20accompanying%20you%20to%20get%20home.%20You%20are%20in%20a%20safe%20place.%20I%20am%20here%20to%20take%20care%20of%20you%3B%20you%20are%20safe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20soldiers%20must%20then%20try%20to%20ensure%20the%20children%20are%20physically%20safe%20but%20ask%20permission%20before%20touching%20them.%20Questions%20include%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BAre%20you%20cold%20or%20hot%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BAre%20you%20thirsty%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BCan%20I%20give%20you%20a%20hand%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BIs%20it%20oka