%26quot%3BA%20publication's%20work%20can't%20be%20treated%20as%20a%20gospel%20of%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Organised%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%20(OCCRP)%2C%20funded%20by%20billionaire%20George%20Soros%2C%20had%20alleged%20insider%20trading%20in%20the%20Adani%20Group%20via%20two%20foreign%20investors.%20The%20Adani%20Group%20has%20called%20them%20%26quot%3Brecycled%20allegations%26quot%3B%20and%20another%20concerted%20bid%20by%20Soros-funded%20interests%20supported%20by%20a%20section%20of%20the%20foreign%20media%20to%20revive%20the%20%26quot%3Bmeritless%20Hindenburg%20report%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExperts%20speak%20to%20NDTV%20on%20the%20development%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Supreme%20Court%20very%20rightly%20pointed%20out%20three%20important%20questions%20to%20the%20petitioner's%20counsel.%20The%20court%20said%20look%2C%20when%20you%20take%20information%20from%20random%20public%20places%2C%20you%20should%20check%20it.%20It%20is%20easy%20to%20make%20allegations%20cooked%20up%20outside%20this%20country...%20The%20expert%20committee%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20already%20said%20there%20is%20no%20evidence%20of%20regulatory%20failure.%20They%20(petitioners)%20are%20relying%20on%20newspaper%20reports%20and%20other%20material%2C%20but%20where%20is%20the%20evidence%3F%20The%20report%20(by%20the%20George%20Soros-backed%20group)%20was%20meant%20to%20destabilise%20the%20country.%26quot%3B%3Cem%3E%20-%20Ashwani%20Dubey%2C%20lawyer%2C%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20is%20that%20the%20petitioners%20had%20approached%20the%20court%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20Hindenburg%20report...%20Essentially%2C%20what%20is%20happening%20is%20that%20after%20the%20court%20appointed%20the%20panel%2C%20the%20petitioners%20have%20now%20come%20up%20with%20questioning%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20panel%20members%2C%20which%20the%20court%20today%20said%20is%20not%20correct.%20The%20Congress%20party%20has%20been%20raising%20the%20issue%20on%20many%20platforms.%20I%20don't%20see%20this%20gaining%20any%20traction...%20This%20has%20the%20potential%20of%20becoming%20Rafale%202.0%20for%20the%20Congress%20by%20barking%20up%20the%20wrong%20tree...%20When%20the%20petitioners%20are%20talking%20about%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20panel%20and%20conflict%20of%20interest%2C%20they%20should%20also%20be%20wary%20of%20the%20conflict%20of%20interest%20of%20the%20people%20who%20prepared%20the%20(Hindenburg)%20report.%20So%20we%20can't%20give%20clean%20chit%20to%20the%20people%20who%20have%20prepared%20the%20report.%20They%20don't%20have%20honest%20intention.%20This%20report%20was%20predominantly%20used%20by%20shortsellers%20to%20make%20money.%20The%20SEBI%20has%20regulations%20to%20protect%20the%20interest%20of%20small%20investors...%26quot%3B%20%3Cem%3E-%20Amitabh%20Tiwari%2C%20political%20analysts%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiven%20a%20choice%2C%20I%20would%20say%20that%20one%20can't%20file%20false%20charges%20against%20anybody%2C%20but%20levelling%20charges%20against%20regulated%20institutions%20and%20statutory%20bodies%20is%20more%20serious.%20Anybody%20and%20anyone%20who%20does%20this%20should%20have%20concrete%20proof.%20The%20court%20was%20very%20clear%20the%20charges%20levelled%20have%20no%20basis.%20The%20intent%20and%20timing%20of%20the%20report%20was%20suspicious%2C%20I%20have%20been%20saying%20from%20the%20start...%26quot%3B%20%3Cem%3E-%20JN%20Gupta%2C%20former%20executive%20director%2C%20SEBI%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20They%20(petitioners)%20are%20asking%20for%20a%20fishing%20inquiry.%20It%20is%20never%20permitted%20in%20a%20court%2C%20that%20they%20make%20an%20allegation%20and%20we%20go%20and%20find%20evidence.%20That%20kind%20of%20thing%20is%20never%20permitted%20in%20court.%20This%20was%20exactly%20politically%20motivated.%20The%20credibility%20of%20SEBI%20was%20upheld.%20It%20is%20doing%20a%20perfect%20job...%20Hindenburg%2C%20we%20all%20know%2C%20is%20a%20short%20seller%2C%20who%20targeted%20Adani.%20We%20need%20to%20be%20careful.%20You%20also%20saw%20Mahua%20Moitra%20matter%20where%20Adani%20was%20targeted...%26quot%3B%20-%20%3Cem%3EDesh%20Ratan%20Nigam%2C%20lawyer%2C%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700847600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2F9o3c5jig_sebi-reuters_625x300_15_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcant-be-fishing-inquiry-experts-to-ndtv-on-hindenburg-case-petitioners-4604092%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Friday%20raised%20tough%20questions%20against%20petitioners%20in%20the%20case%20linked%20to%20a%20report%20by%20a%20George%20Soros-funded%20group%20that%20targeted%20the%20Adani%20Group.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcant-be-fishing-inquiry-experts-to-ndtv-on-hindenburg-case-petitioners-4604092%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcant-be-fishing-inquiry-experts-to-ndtv-on-hindenburg-case-petitioners-4604092%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcant-be-fishing-inquiry-experts-to-ndtv-on-hindenburg-case-petitioners-4604092%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Market%20regulator%20Sebi%20proposes%20easing%20trading%20plans%20for%20company%20insiders%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700847340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-10%2F13%2Ffull%2F1697213648-3949.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fmarket-regulator-sebi-plans-overhaul-of-insider-trading-plan-framework-123112400982_1.html%22%2C%22summary%2