0visa%20renewals%20for%20Afghan%20diplomats%2C%20let%20alone%20considering%20their%20continued%20presence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20October%201%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fas-of-october-1-afghanistan-embassy-in-new-delhi-stands-closed%5C%22%3Eshut%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20MEA%20had%20claimed%20that%20the%20embassy%20was%20still%20operating%20normally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20on%20Friday%20morning%2C%20the%20Afghan%20embassy%20again%20issued%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FFMamundzay%2Fstatus%2F1727862940827525408%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they%20were%20%E2%80%9Cpermanently%E2%80%9D%20closing%20down%20the%20embassy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20answer%20to%20queries%20from%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20Islamic%20Republic-appointed%20Afghan%20ambassador%20to%20India%2C%20Farid%20Mamundzay%2C%20replied%20that%20while%20the%20embassy%20had%20%E2%80%9Coperationally%20closed%E2%80%9D%20on%20October%201%2C%20but%20%E2%80%9Con%20an%20emergency%20basis%2C%20we%20did%20provide%20some%20services%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAdditionally%2C%20my%20colleagues%20temporarily%20closed%20the%20mission%20in%20protest%20over%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20with%20the%20hope%20that%20it%20would%20change%2C%20and%20they%20would%20be%20granted%20visas.%20Unfortunately%2C%20neither%20of%20these%20expectations%20materialized%2C%20leading%20us%20to%20the%20decision%20to%20permanently%20shut%20down%20the%20Republic%20mission%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mamundzay%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20in%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20evening%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20wheels%20had%20been%20spinning%20behind%20the%20scenes.%20The%20two%20senior%20Afghan%20diplomats%20posted%20in%20other%20cities%2C%20had%20announced%20that%20they%20had%20already%20taken%20over%20the%20embassy.%20A%20press%20statement%20stated%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9CConsul%20Generals%20of%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%20of%20Afghanistan%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Ms.%20Zakia%20Wardak%20and%20Acting%20Consul%20General%20of%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%20of%20Afghanistan%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20Mr.%20Sayed%20Mohammad%20Ibrahimkhil%20have%20assumed%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20Embassy%20of%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%20of%20Afghanistan%2C%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EPress%20Statement%20by%20the%20consul%20general%20of%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%20of%20Afghanistan%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20Acting%20Consul%20General%20of%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%20of%20Afghanistan%20in%20Hyderabad%20regards%20closing%20of%20Afghanistan%20Embassy%20in%20New%20Delhi-%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FHmCZcIaBFE%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FHmCZcIaBFE%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Zakia%20Wardak%20(%40ZakiaWardak)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZakiaWardak%2Fstatus%2F1728016816596021398%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2024%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20no%20official%20response%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20learnt%20that%20the%20two%20Afghan%20diplomats%20had%20been%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Friday%20and%20visited%20the%20embassy%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20there%20are%20no%20plans%20to%20alter%20the%20name%20of%20the%20embassy%2C%20and%20the%20red%2C%20black%20and%20white%20flag%20of%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%20will%20remain%20hoisted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20asked%20Ibrahimkhil%20if%20he%20had%20physically%20started%20to%20work%20at%20the%20Embassy%2C%20he%20was%20on%20way%20to%20the%20airport%20and%20sat%20that%20he%20will%20be%20back%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20from%20the%20two%20CGs%20also%20asks%20the%20%E2%80%9Cformer%20Afghan%20Ambassador%20and%20former%20Afghan%20diplomats%2Fofficials%20to%20kindly%20not%20use%20the%20social%20media%20platforms%20of%20the%20Embassy%20of%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%20of%20Afghanistan%2C%20New%20Delhi%20for%20issuing%20any%20unwarranted%2C%20irresponsible%20and%20unprofessional%20statements%2Fpress%20releases%20from%20abroad%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20said%20they%20were%20in%20%E2%80%9Cconstant%20touch%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20MEA%20to%20%E2%80%9Caddress%20the%20current%20dif%EF%AC%81cult%20situation%20wherein%20most%20of%20our%20former%20Embassy%20colleagues%20have%20received%20asylum%20and%20left%20India%2C%20therefore%2C%20we%20are%20facing%20shortage%20of%20diplomatic%20and%20of%EF%AC%81cial%20staff%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Ftaliban-foreign-ministry-replaces-afghan-ambassador-in-new-delhi-but-embassy-issues-denial%5C%22%3EIn%20May%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20the%20Taliban%20regime%20had%20issued%20a%20directive%20seeking%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20current%20Afghan%20ambassador%20to%20India%2C%20appointed%20by%20the%20previous%20Islamic%20Republic%2C%20and%20replacing%20them%20with%20another%20diplomat%20in%20the%20role%20of%20Charge%20D%E2%80%99affaires.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attempt%20proved%20unsuccessful%2C%20as%20the%20diplomat%20appointed%20by%20the%20Taliban%20was%20prevented%20from%20assuming%20the%20position%20by%20other%20colleagues%20at%20that%20time.%20Nevertheless%2C%20Ambassador%20Farid%20Mamundzay%20hinted%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20official%20silence%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20suggested%20that%20New%20Delhi%20would%20prefer%20a%20change%20in%20the%20leadership%20at%20the%20embassy%2C%20to%20one%20which%20was%20more%20aligned%20with%20the%20Taliban%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20have%20also%20been%20a%20bit%20more%20difficult%20publicly%20to%20recognise%20Qadir%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20role%20since%20he%20had%20moved%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20an%20appointment%20letter%20from%20Kabul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20in%20line%20with%20the%20international%20community%2C%20does%20not%20acknowledge%20the%20Taliban%20regime.%20However%2C%20in%20June%202022%2C%20India%20deployed%20a%20technical%20team%20comprising%20diplomats%20and%20security%20personnel%20to%20Kabul.%20This%20move%20signified%20India%E2%80%99s%20re-entry%20into%20the%20Afghan%20capital%2C%20following%20the%20complete%20evacuation%20of%20the%20embassy%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20Taliban%E2%80%99s%20takeover%20of%20Kabul%20in%20August%202021.%20The%20technical%20team%20operates%20as%20the%20de-facto%20embassy%20of%20India%20in%20Kabul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20marked%20the%20public%20change%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20attitude%20towards%20the%20Taliban%2C%20with%20New%20Delhi%20reaching%20out%20to%20the%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Afghan%20diplomats%20in%20the%20embassy%20had%20been%20receiving%20a%20frosty%20reception%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20Consul%20Generals%20who%20met%20frequently%20with%20senior%20MEA%20officials%20to%20discuss%20issues%20related%20to%20Afghans%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20consul%20generals%20from%20the%20two%20consulates%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20Hyderabad%20actively%20participated%20in%20meetings%20chaired%20by%20the%20Taliban%20foreign%20minister%2C%20Amir%20Khan%20Muttaqi%2C%20in%20contrast%20to%20their%20counterparts%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20who%20disregarded%20instructions%20from%20Kabul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20official%20sources%20highlighted%20that%20they%20were%20both%20appointed%20by%20the%20previous%20government%20and%20described%20this%20change%20as%20an%20internal%20matter%20between%20the%20Afghan%20diplomats.%20They%20also%20said%20that%20one%20of%20the%20two%20Consular%20G