0parts%20of%20the%20constituency%2C%20like%20Badpipli%2C%20Diya%20Kumari%20highlights%20both%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ework%20that%20her%20family%20has%20done%20as%20erstwhile%20rulers%20and%20her%20own%20work%20as%20MP%20of%20Rajsamand.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20candidate%20named%20in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20very%20first%20list%2C%20Diya%20has%20had%20a%20long%20time%20to%20campaign%20and%20f%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eob%20off%20controversies.%20With%20polling%20round%20the%20corner%2C%20talk%20of%20her%20as%20a%20possible%20chief%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eministerial%20candidate%2C%20an%20alternative%20to%20Vasundhraje%20has%20grown%20with%20headlines%20like%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKaun%20hai%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Evoh%20Rajkumari%20joh%20ban%20saktee%20hai%20Rajasthan%20kee%20Rani%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(Which%20of%20the%20princesses%20will%20become%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ERajasthan%E2%80%99s%20queen)%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20are%20talking%20about%20Diya%20Kumari%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20but%20we%20say%20she%20won%E2%80%99t%20even%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ebecome%20an%20MLA%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gopichand%20Aggarwal%2C%20a%20shop-keeper%20and%20a%20supporter%20of%20Sitaram%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAgarwala%2C%20the%20Congress%20candidate%20from%20Vidhyadhar%20Nagar%2C%20%E2%80%9CJust%20being%20from%20royalty%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20assure%20you%20of%20votes%2C%20India%20is%20a%20loktantrik%20country%2C%20not%20a%20kingdom.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESitaram%20Agarwal%2C%20treasurer%20of%20the%20Rajasthan%20Pradesh%20Congress%20Committee%20is%20a%20local%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ebusinessman%20who%20lost%20to%20Narpat%20Singh%20Rajvi%20in%202018.%20In%20several%20interviews%20Agarwal%20has%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Epointed%20out%20the%20contributing%20factor%20to%20that%20loss%20was%20rebel%20candidate%2C%20Vikram%20Singh%20