illusioned%2C%20defeated%20and%20bitter.%20We%20also%20see%20him%20doting%20on%20his%20daughter%2C%20arguing%20in%20good%20faith%20with%20abusive%20trolls%20and%20looking%20distracted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShukla%E2%80%99s%20film%20is%20a%20stirring%20portrait%20of%20a%20time%20when%20TV%20news%20has%20exceeded%20all%20limits%20of%20parody.%20Shukla%20has%20likened%20the%20film%20to%20the%20Titanic%20%E2%80%93%20where%20an%20entire%20industry%20is%20slowly%20sinking%20into%20the%20abyss%20right%20in%20front%20of%20our%20eyes.%20To%20his%20credit%2C%20however%2C%20what%20could%20have%20been%20a%20more%20hysterical%20film%20is%20largely%20meditative%20and%20introspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20documentary%20feature%20had%20its%20world%20premiere%20at%20the%202022%20Toronto%20International%20Film%20Festival%20(TIFF)%2C%20its%20India%20premiere%20at%20the%202023%20Jio%20MAMI%20Mumbai%20International%20Film%20Festival%20and%20played%20at%20the%20recently%20concluded%202023%20Dharamshala%20International%20Film%20Festival%2C%20among%20many%20other%20festivals%20across%20the%20globe.%20Having%20been%20on%20the%20radar%20for%20over%2014%20months%2C%20Shukla%20says%20he%E2%80%99s%20yet%20to%20receive%20a%20%E2%80%9Cterm%20sheet%E2%80%9D%20from%20a%20streaming%20platform%20or%20a%20distributor.%20But%20he%E2%80%99s%20no%20stranger%20to%20these%20pre-release%20struggles%2C%20given%20how%20his%20earlier%20film%20%3Cem%3EAn%20Insignificant%20Man%3C%2Fem%3E%20(which%20he%20co-directed%20with%20Khushboo%20Ranka)%20also%20faced%20a%20lengthy%20battle%20with%20the%20censors%2C%20before%20it%20released%20theatrically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Shukla%20speaks%20about%20finding%20a%20narrative%20by%20scouring%20through%20hundreds%20of%20hours%20of%20footage%20and%20shaping%20a%20film%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20merely%20engage%20with%20its%20echo%20chamber%2C%20and%20other%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEdited%20excerpts%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWas%20there%20a%20specific%20moment%20when%20you%20decided%20on%20your%20film%20being%20about%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3Es%20rapidly-deteriorating%20TV%20media%3F%20How%20did%20Ravish%20Kumar%20become%20the%20protagonist%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20reading%20a%20news%20article%20%E2%80%93%20I%20think%20it%20was%20a%20%3Cem%3ENewslaundry%3C%2Fem%3E%20piece%20in%202018%2C%20which%20had%20a%20headline%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2Fndtv-liquidates-7-38-stake-in-subsidiary-to-pay-office-rent%5C%22%3ENDTV%20liquidates%207.38%25%20stake%20in%20subsidiary%20to%20pay%20office%20rent%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%20I%20was%20caught%20off%20guard%20that%20NDTV%20%E2%80%93%20an%20institution%20which%20was%20such%20a%20regular%20fixture%20during%20my%20growing%20up%20years%20%E2%80%93%20is%20in%20trouble.%20So%2C%20I%20remember%20my%20first%20question%20was%20%E2%80%93%20why%20is%20this%20happening%3F%20Who%20is%20this%20Ravish%20guy%2C%20berating%20his%20audience%3F%20And%20what%20is%20really%20going%20on%20in%20the%20NDTV%20offices%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20came%20across%20Ravish%20(Kumar)%20in%20a%20phase%20where%20he%20was%20very%20contemplative%20while%20being%20on%20air.%20Instead%20of%20praising%20his%20audiences%2C%20which%20is%20what%20prime-time%20anchors%20often%20do%2C%20he%20would%20criticise%20his%20audience%2C%20telling%20them%20how%20they%20weren%E2%80%99t%20doing%20enough.%20He%20was%20on%20TV%2C%20and%20he%20was%20asking%20his%20audience%20to%20stop%20watching%20TV.%20It%20was%20highly%20unusual%2C%20and%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20great%20starting%20point%20of%20inquiry%20into%20the%20lives%20of%20those%20working%20in%20TV%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20like%20how%20even%20in%20a%20bleak%20film%20like%20this%2C%20you%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3Eve%20still%20managed%20to%20retain%20a%20sense%20of%20humour%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3Ethe%20scene%20where%20Ravish%20Kumar%20seems%20distracted%20during%20a%20celebratory%20cake%20being%20cut%20in%20his%20office%2C%20for%20example%20%E2%80%93%20it%20almost%20become%20a%20metronome%20for%20the%20narrative.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20340px)%2085vw%2C%20340px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24204824%2FVinay-Shukla.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22340%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24204824%2FVinay-Shukla.jpg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24204824%2FVinay-Shukla-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24204824%2FVinay-Shukla-768x1024.jpg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686286%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22454%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EVinay%20Shukla.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cake-cutting%20scenes%20were%20my%20homage%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EGodfather%3C%2Fem%3E%20films.%20Usually%20when%20there%20are%20oranges%20on%20screen%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EGodfather%3C%2Fem%3E%20films%2C%20something%20ominous%20happens%20soon%20after.%20The%20cinema%20student%20in%20me%20always%20had%20this%20in%20the%20back%20of%20my%20head%20that%20I%E2%80%99d%20love%20to%20do%20something%20similar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20came%20across%20a%20cake%20cutting%20on%20the%20first%20day%20that%20I%20was%20shooting%20in%20the%20NDTV%20office%3A%20you%20could%20immediately%20tell%20the%20air%20was%20heavy%2C%20and%20someone%20was%20leaving%20in%20less-than-ideal%20circumstances.%20People%2C%20who%20had%20probably%20been%20at%20this%20job%20for%2020-25%20years%2C%20were%20asked%20to%20go%20search%20for%20a%20new%20job%20out%20of%20the%20blue.%20I%20understood%20that%20what%20was%20happening%20around%20the%20cake%20cutting%20was%20poignant.%20I%20saw%20so%20many%20cakes%20being%20cut%2C%20and%20I%20somewhere%20wanted%20people%E2%80%99s%20attention%20back%20to%20the%20crisis%20within%20the%20news%20industry.%20Somewhere%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20become%20desensitised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3Eve%20often%20spoken%20about%20the%20film%20being%20like%20that%20day%20on%20the%20Titanic%2C%20where%20musicians%20were%20playing%20even%20as%20the%20ship%20was%20going%20down.%20Would%20that%20make%20the%20cake-cutting%20the%20equivalent%20to%20those%20life-boats%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENice%20line%2C%20I%20think%20I%E2%80%99ll%20start%20using%20it%20as%20my%20own!%20I%E2%80%99ve%20met%20cricket%20journalists%20and%20film%20journalists%2C%20who%20are%20finding%20it%20hard%20to%20go%20against%20mainstream%20narratives%20set%20by%20the%20people%20in%20power.%20Very%20often%2C%20people%20get%20obsessed%20with%20the%20politics%20of%20this%20film%2C%20which%20is%20there%2C%20but%20if%20you%E2%80%99re%20looking%20at%20building%20better%20systems%20%E2%80%93%20the%20conversation%20is%20so%20large.%20I%20showed%20this%20film%20to%20a%20friend%20who%20runs%20a%20medical%20startup%20%E2%80%93%20and%20he%20said%20that%20I%20had%20managed%20to%20condense%20the%20startup%20life.%20Everyone%20keeps%20telling%20you%20you%E2%80%99re%20bleeding%20too%20much%20cash%2C%20someone%20is%20poaching%20your%20employees%2C%20and%20you%E2%80%99re%20literally%20just%20soldiering%20on%20because%20you%20believe%20in%20something.%20%3Cem%3EWhile%20We%20Watched%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20about%20the%20loneliness%20of%20being%20an%20idealist%20%E2%80%93%20people%20who%20choose%20to%20believe%2C%20and%20persevere%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWas%20it%20hard%20to%20find%20a%20flaw%20in%20Ravish%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3Eto%20make%20him%20seem%20more%20human%20than%20an%20ideal%3F%20Did%20you%20manage%20to%20crack%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20Ravish%20is%20an%20ideal%20in%20the%20film.%20It%20starts%20off%20with%20him%20saying%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20give%20up!%E2%80%9D%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20great%20way%20to%20introduce%20a%20%E2%80%98hero%E2%80%99.%20A%20lot%20of%20people%20in%20the%20West%2C%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20who%20Ravish%20was%2C%20they%20asked%20who%20this%20guy%20was%20and%20why%20he%20was%20so%20negative.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20tried%20to%20build%20a%20portrait%20of%20where%20Ravish%20is%20at%2C%20vis-a-vis%20his%20contemplations%20about%20where%20TV%20journalism%20is%20at.%20There%20are%20scenes%2C%20when%20you%20see%20him%20on%20stage%20against%20a%20teacher%2C%20and%20people%20have%20told%20me%20how%20they%E2%80%99ve%20interpreted%20the%20scene%20as%20where%20Ravish%20knows%20to%20get%20the%20people%20behind%20him%2C%20while%20the%20teacher%20doesn%E2%80%99t.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EKya%20aapko%20aisa%20Hindustan%20chahiye%20tha%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%E2%80%9D%20And%20the%20audience%20responds%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ENahi%3C%2Fem%3E!%E2%80%9D%20He%20knows%20how%20to%20run%20the%20audience.%20Also%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20scene%20where%20he%20gets%20angry%20at%20his%20producer%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20broadcast.%20There%20are%20moments%20when%20people%20are%20leaving%2C%20it%20has%20subtle%20commentary%20about%20Ravish%20as%20a%20person%20within%20the%20film.%20People%20looking%20for%20a%20hero%20in%20the%20film%20will%20always%20find%20one.%20And%20similarly%20with%20someone%20who%20is%20looking%20for%20someone%20less%2C%20will%20also%20find%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWere%20you%20ever%20concerned%20that%20the%20film%20might%20not%20find%20an%20audience%20outside%20Ravish%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3Es%20echo%20chamber%3F%20Did%20you%20make%20any%20specific%20choices%20for%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo.%20I%20think%20my%20intention%20was%20always%20to%20make%20the%20best%20film%20possible%2C%20for%20an%20audience%20that%20you%20care%20about.%20If%20the%20film%20is%20on%20solid%20ground%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20potent%20%E2%80%93%20it%20will%20make%20its%20way%20in%20all%20directions.%20I%20can%20do%20certain%20things%20as%20a%20filmmaker%2C%20make%20certain%20choices.%20But%20if%20only%20the%20choir%20gets%20what%20I%20want%20to%20say%20then%20the%20problem%20is%20with%20my%20messaging%2C%20and%20not%20the%20people.%20The%20story%20has%20to%20stand%20on%20its%20legs%2C%20if%20that%20happens%20then%20the%20message%20will%20get%20across.%20Which%20filmmaker%20wants%20to%20limit%20their%20audience%2C%20%3Cem%3Eyaar%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%20We%20all%20want%20to%20show%20our%20films%20to%20as%20many%20people%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20make%20my%20films%20with%20a%20clear%20understanding%20that%20I%20want%20my%20family%20and%20friends%20to%20watch%20and%20enjoy%20it.%20I%E2%80%99m%20very%20close%20to%20them%2C%20and%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20we%E2%80%99re%20very%20dissimilar.%20When%20I%20speak%20to%20them%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20exercising%20a%20certain%20emotional%20vocabulary%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20I%20also%20exercise%20while%20making%20the%20film.%20My%20own%20family%20goes%20and%20watches%20each%20and%20every%20film%20out%20there%2C%20has%20voted%20for%20every%20major%20party%2C%20and%20my%20litmus%20test%20is%20if%20my%20family%20and%20friends%20can%20engage%20with%20the%20film%20then%20the%20audience%20outside%20will%20engage%20with%20it%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20you%20hopeful%20about%20releasing%20the%20film%20widely%20in%20India%3F%20How%20do%20you%20plan%20on%20doing%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%E2%80%99m%20always%20hopeful.%20The%20film%20recently%20just%20had%20its%20India%20premiere%20(at%20MAMI)%2C%20and%20I%20will%20now%20approach%20both%20theatres%20and%20streaming%20services.%20I%E2%80%99m%20in%20conversation%20with%20everyone%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20all%20given%20me%20a%20lot%20of%20love%20for%20the%20film%2C%20but%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20an%20offer%20from%20any%20platform%20yet.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20met%20every%20streamer%20in%20town.%20People%20are%20aware%20of%20my%20work%2C%20streaming%20services%20looking%20to%20do%20non-fiction%20work%20%E2%80%93%20I%E2%80%99m%20the%20first%20person%20they%E2%80%99ll%20call.%20I%20have%20many%20friends%20there%2C%20but%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20term-sheet%20from%20any%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%E2%80%99ll%20also%20say%20this%2C%20which%20I%20tell%20many%20others.%20This%20entire%20film%20distribution%20set-up%20via%20theatres%20and%20streaming%20platforms%20%E2%80%93%20we%E2%80%99re%20a%20part%20of%20it.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20take%20pot-shots%20at%20streaming%20services%20and%20theatrical%20distributors%2C%20pointing%20fingers%20that%20they%20are%20the%20problem.%20We%20need%20to%20zoom%20out%20and%20see%20the%20problem%20with%20the%20culture%20at%20large.%20The%20audience%20also%20has%20to%20pick%20up%20some%20responsibility%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESome%20of%20your%20colleagues%20like%20Payal%20Kapadia%2C%20Rintu%2BSushmit%20weren%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3Et%20able%20to%20release%20their%20films%20in%20India.%20What%20gives%20you%20the%20encouragement%20to%20keep%20going%20in%20such%20times%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadness.%20Filmmakers%2C%20especially%20in%20India%2C%20are%20a%20crazy%20bunch!%20Why%20do%20we%20want%20to%20do%20this%3F%20Because%20we%20feel%20like%20it!%20There%E2%80%99s%20no%20rationale%20or%20logic%20here.%20Why%20are%20you%20investing%204-5%20years%20into%20a%20film%20that%20might%20not%20get%20a%20wide%20release%3F%20You%20do%20things%20because%20it%20feels%20like%20the%20right%20thing%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETher