0to%20act%20as%20the%20gatekeeper%20but%20not%20allowed%20to%20speak.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20random%20excerpts%20of%20individual%20audiences%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERahul%20Dravid%20was%20first%20on%20the%20list.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPM%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Rahul%20%3Cem%3Ebhai%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Is%20there%20any%20explanation%3F%20I%20am%20told%20you%20were%20distracted%20doing%20all%20those%20ads%20for%20some%20engine%20oil.%20That%20is%20not%20your%20job.%20Leave%20such%20marketing%20matters%20to%20Amitabh%20%3Cem%3Ebhai%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDravid%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Sir%2C%20I%20am%20disappointed%2C%20too.%20I%20must%20share%20that%20in%20private%20I%20had%20argued%20very%20strongly%20that%20for%20the%20final%20match%20you%20should%20have%20been%20named%20the%20coach.%20Your%20understanding%20of%20tactics%20and%20reading%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehawa%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20superb.%20But%20I%20was%20overruled%20by%20the%20BCCI%20bosses%2C%20citing%20some%20ICC%20rules%20against%20involvement%20of%20governmental%20functionaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVirat%20Kohli%20is%20next.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPM%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Virat.%20How%20is%20Anushka%20taking%20the%20loss%3F%20Why%20did%20you%20go%20so%20slow%3F%20I%20was%20expecting%20a%20century%20from%20you.%20Had%20we%20won%2C%20I%20would%20have%20named%20Ashram%20Road%20after%20you.%20We%20have%20had%20enough%20of%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVirat%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Sir%2C%20you%20have%20always%20been%20a%20source%20of%20inspiration%20not%20just%20for%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20but%20for%20the%20entire%20nation.%20We%20had%20all%20urged%20Rahul%20sir%20to%20rope%20you%20in%20as%20the%20coach%20for%20the%20final.%20But%20I%20suspect%20some%20conspiracy%20against%20you.%20The%20BCCI%20bosses%20were%20bent%20on%20denying%20us%20the%20benefit%20of%20your%20guidance.%20We%20all%20remember%20the%20brilliant%20way%20you%20guided%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20pilots%20on%20how%20to%20attack%20terror%20infrastructure%20in%20POK.%20By%20the%20way%2C%20sir%2C%20I%20hope%20you%20are%20being%20consulted%20by%20the%20Israeli%20Air%20Force%20planners%20in%20their%20campaign%20against%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERohit%20Sharma%2C%20the%20captain%2C%20was%20next%20on%20the%20list.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPM%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Rohit.%20Before%20you%20say%20what%20happened%2C%20I%20want%20to%20know%20why%20you%20did%20not%20invite%20me%20to%20your%20wedding%2C%20just%20as%20Virat%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERohit%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Sir%2C%20I%20am%20not%20a%20celebrity%20or%20exhibitionist%20like%20Virat.%20I%20was%20not%20marrying%20a%20celebrity.%20My%20marriage%20was%20my%20affair%2C%20a%20private%20one.%20But%2C%20as%20Rahul%20sir%20must%20have%20told%20you%2C%20I%20was%20very%20keen%20to%20have%20your%20guidance%20in%20the%20dressing%20room.%20Nobody%20can%20read%20the%20pitch%20as%20you%20do%2C%20whatever%20the%20arena.%20Nobody%20can%20out-strategise%20the%20rivals%20as%20you%20do.%20Honestly%2C%20sir%2C%20I%20felt%20the%20absence%20of%20your%20guidance%20when%20Head%20was%20refusing%20to%20vacate%20the%20crease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERavindra%20Jadeja%20is%20ushered%20in%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPM%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20%3Cem%3E(In%20Gujarati)%3C%2Fem%3E%20Your%20wife%20is%20our%20MLA.%20You%20are%20one%20of%20us.%20Please%20tell%20me%20why%20we%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJadeja%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Saheb%2C%20it%20is%20simple.%20I%20think%20you%20have%20enemies%20hovering%20around%20you.%20The%20entire%20team%20was%20pleading%20for%20your%20ball-to-ball%20guidance.%20But%20the%20BCCI%20brass%20has%20its%20own%20calculations.%20I%20am%20not%20sure%2C%20but%20I%20feel%20in%20my%20bones%20that%20somehow%20the%20bookies%20ensured%20that%20we%20did%20not%20have%20your%20guidance.%20The%20nexus%20between%20th