%20as%20Vibhuti%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%20assaulted%20Dalsaniya.%20Subsequently%2C%20Vibhuti%20Patel%2C%20Parixit%20Patel%20(a%20manager%20at%20Raniba%20Industries)%2C%20and%20four%20others%20also%20joined%20in%20the%20assault.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20the%20group%20dragged%20Dalsaniya%20to%20an%20elevator%2C%20took%20him%20to%20the%20terrace%20of%20the%20commercial%20building%2C%20and%20beat%20him%20up%20with%20a%20belt%20while%20also%20kicking%20and%20punching%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CVibhuti%20Patel%20forced%20me%20to%20take%20her%20%3Cem%3Echappal%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20my%20mouth%20and%20made%20me%20apologise%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dalsaniya%20said%20in%20his%20complaint.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20threatened%20to%20kill%20me%20if%20I%20came%20to%20Ravapar%20Road%20or%20dared%20to%20file%20a%20complaint.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20incident%2C%20Dalsaniya%20was%20admitted%20to%20the%20state-run%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vibesofindia.com%2Fmaya-sharmas-new-book-explores-the-lives-of-marginalised-lgbt-women-in-gujarat%2F%5C%22%3EGujarat%3C%2Fa%3E%20Medical%20Education%20and%20Research%20Society%20Hospital%20in%20Morbi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVibhuti%20Patel%20and%20her%20employees%20have%20been%20booked%20under%20various%20sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%20including%20Sections%20323%20(voluntarily%20causing%20hurt)%2C%20504%20(intentional%20insult%20with%20intent%20to%20provoke%20breach%20of%20the%20peace)%2C%20506(2)%20(criminal%20intimidation)%2C%20143%20(unlawful%20assembly)%2C%20147%20(rioting)%2C%20and%20149%20(every%20member%20of%20an%20unlawful%20assembly%20guilty%20of%20the%20offence%20committed%20in%20prosecution%20of%20a%20common%20object).%20The%20Scheduled%20Caste%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%20has%20also%20been%20invoked%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gujarat%20Police%20are%20currently%20investigating%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3