ious%20regulatory%20norms.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Frbi-slaps-penalties-totalling-rs-10-34-cr-on-citibank-bob-and-iob-123112400796_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Frbi-slaps-penalties-totalling-rs-10-34-cr-on-citibank-bob-and-iob-123112400796_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Frbi-slaps-penalties-totalling-rs-10-34-cr-on-citibank-bob-and-iob-123112400796_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mystery%20Around%20Mamata%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20Fresh%20Investment%20Call%20for%20Tajpur%20Port%20Assigned%20to%20Adani%20a%20Year%20Ago%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24180126%2FF_drvO5bUAA2B-n.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKolkata%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0West%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20during%20the%20annual%20flagship%20business%20event%20Bengal%20Global%20Business%20Summit%20(BGBS)%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwfpbeP5nsSE%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20Tuesday%20that%20fresh%20tenders%20would%20be%20issued%20for%20the%20development%20of%20a%20deep%20sea%20port%20at%20Tajpur%2C%20for%20which%20the%20state%20government%20had%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAdaniKaran%2Fstatus%2F1580217290020511746%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%3Ehanded%20over%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0a%20Letter%20of%20Intent%20(LoI)%20to%20the%20Adani%20Ports%20and%20Special%20Economic%20Zone%20(APSEZ)%20last%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20group%20company%20had%20secured%20the%20LoI%20after%20becoming%20the%20highest%20bidder%20for%20the%20project%20and%20was%20awaiting%20the%20Letter%20of%20Award%20(LoA)%20from%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20announcement%20means%20the%20government%20has%20cancelled%20the%20LoI%2C%20senior%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20leader%20Chandrima%20Bhattacharya%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20minister%20of%20state%20(independent%20charge)%20at%20the%20finance%20department%2C%20said%20only%20commerce%20and%20industries%20minister%20Shashi%20Panja%20will%20comment%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPanja%20has%20not%20responded%20to%20calls%20and%20a%20WhatsApp%20message%20from%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20report%20will%20be%20updated%20once%20a%20response%20is%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmails%20have%20also%20been%20sent%20to%20the%20Adani%20group%20and%20to%20APSEZ%20chief%20executive%20officer%20(CEO-ports)%2C%20Subrat%20Tripathy%2C%20asking%20if%20the%20government%20has%20communicated%20anything%20to%20them%20and%20if%20they%20have%20any%20comment%20to%20make.%20No%20response%20has%20been%20received%20till%20the%20filing%20of%20this%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBanerjee%E2%80%99s%20announcement%20triggered%20curiosity%20among%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20political%20and%20business%20circles%2C%20as%20Adani%20group%20head%20Gautam%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20Karan%2C%20had%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adaniports.com%2F-%2Fmedia%2FProject%2FPorts%2FInvestor%2FTranscripts%2FQ2-FY24-Earnings-Call-transcript.pdf%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0only%20a%20few%20days%20before%20the%20BGBS%20that%20the%20group%20was%20%E2%80%9Cstill%20waiting%20for%E2%80%9D%20the%20LoA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20received%20the%20letter%20of%20intent.%20We%20are%20waiting%20for%20LOA%20to%20come.%20Once%20we%20get%20(it)%2C%20it%20will%20be%2018%20to%2024%20months%20before%20we%20start%20any%20construction%20over%20there%20since%20we%20have%20to%20go%20through%20the%20EC%20(environment%20clearance)%20as%20well%20as%20groundwork%20over%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adaniports.com%2F-%2Fmedia%2FProject%2FPorts%2FInvestor%2FTranscripts%2FQ2-FY24-Earnings-Call-transcript.pdf%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20November%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20days%20later%2C%20on%20November%2014%2C%20Panja%20told%20journalists%20in%20New%20Delhi%20that%20they%20did%20not%20want%20%E2%80%9Cpolitics%20to%20overtake%20development%E2%80%9D.%20However%2C%20her%20version%20on%20its%20status%20was%20different%20from%20that%20of%20Karan%20Adani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20LoI%20was%20given%20to%20them%20and%20now%20we%20are%20waiting%20for%20their%20response.%20There%20are%20certain%20clearances%20that%20the%20government%20of%20India%20gives%20from%20the%20ministry%20of%20shipping%20and%20various%20other%20departments.%20They%20(Adanis)%20must%20be%20working%20on%20those%20certification%20clearances%2C%E2%80%9D%20Panja%20had%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DX0F-DxlgBTw%26t%3D102s%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20top%20bureaucrat%20who%20spoke%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20said%20the%20decision%20to%20make%20a%20fresh%20investment%20call%20was%20taken%20%E2%80%9Cat%20the%20last%20minute%2C%20after%20noticing%20the%20complete%20absence%20of%20the%20Adani%20group%20at%20the%20BGBS%E2%80%9D.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0could%20not%20independently%20verify%20this%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20was%20conspicuous%20by%20its%20absence%20during%20the%20BGBS%2C%20even%20though%20the%20group%20had%20participated%20in%20the%20previous%20editions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20group%20has%20been%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20criticism%20from%20many%20opposition%20parties%2C%20including%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20TMC%2C%20for%20its%20alleged%20proximity%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20irregular%20practices%2C%20including%20stock%20price%20manipulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20early%20months%20following%20Mamata%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20return%20to%20power%20in%202021%20had%20seen%20growing%20proximity%20between%20the%20state%20government%20and%20the%20Adani%20group.%20Gautam%20and%20Karan%20Adani%20had%20separately%20met%20the%20chief%20minister%20on%20different%20occasions%20%E2%80%93%20Gautam%20Adani%20in%20December%202021%20and%20Karan%20Adani%20in%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fkolkata%2Fkaran-adani-meets-west-bengal-cm-mamata-banerjee-chief-secretary-at-nabanna%2Farticleshow%2F89493607.cms%5C%22%3EFebruary%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fmamata-hands-over-tajpur-ports-letter-of-intent-to-karan-adani%2Farticleshow%2F94817328.cms%5C%22%3EOctober%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20after%20meeting%20Banerjee%2C%20Adani%20had%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgautam_adani%2Fstatus%2F1466409022970499073%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20discussed%20%E2%80%9Cdifferent%20investment%20scenarios%20and%20the%20tremendous%20potential%20of%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%9D.%20Five%20months%20later%2C%20at%20the%20previous%20BGBS%20edition%20in%20April%202022%2C%20Adani%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adani.com%2F-%2Fmedia%2FProject%2FAdani%2FMedia-Coverage%2F2022%2F20220421-HBL-Adani-to-invest-over-10000-cr-in-Bengal.pdf%3Fla%3Den%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0the%20summit%20that%20their%20investment%20in%20the%20state%20would%20exceed%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore%20over%20the%20next%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20said%20that%20the%20group%20was%20%E2%80%9Ccommitting%20to%20bring%20technology%20and%20scale%20to%20create%20world-class%20infrastructure%2C%20data%20centres%2C%20centres%20of%20excellence%20for%20digital%20innovation%2C%20under-sea%20cable%20and%20warehousing%20and%20logistics%20park%20in%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20bagging%20the%20LoI%2C%20the%20group%C2%A0%3Ca