g%20time%2C%20have%20disassociated%20yourself%20from%20the%20left%20movement%20and%20the%20student%20movement%20you%20represented.%20I%2C%20along%20with%20others%2C%20despite%20being%20disappointed%2C%20respected%20your%20decision.%20However%2C%20my%20disappointment%20now%20lies%20in%20your%20ever-changing%20positions.%20You%20are%20entitled%20to%20your%20views%2C%20opinions%2C%20and%20constant%20changes%20of%20heart.%20However%2C%20what%20bothers%20me%20is%20the%20heartlessness.%20I%20am%20saying%20this%20not%20from%20the%20position%20of%20being%20a%20former%20JNU%20student%20union%20president%20or%20as%20a%20student%20activist%20whom%20you%20sat%20with%20for%20long%20hours%20debating%2C%20nor%20as%20a%20friend%20who%20has%20several%20pleasant%20memories%20of%20working%20with%20you.%20I%20am%20saying%20this%20from%20a%20moral%2C%20ethical%2C%20and%20political%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20your%20interview%20to%20ANI%2C%20you%20claimed%20that%20you%20had%20this%20sudden%20change%20of%20heart%20after%20seeing%20the%20great%20service%20of%20Modi%20and%20Shah.%20But%20strangely%2C%20you%20conveniently%20remained%20silent%20on%20the%20series%20of%20changes%20of%20heart%20you%20have%20had%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20I%20think%20you%20should%20also%20enlighten%20why%20you%20floated%20a%20party%20only%20to%20dissolve%20it%20later%2C%20and%20why%20you%20decided%20to%20file%20a%20petition%20against%20the%20dilution%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20only%20to%20have%20another%20change%20of%20heart%20and%20withdraw%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20yes%2C%20I%20feel%20disappointed.%20Let%20me%20explain%20why%20I%20feel%20this%20way.%20My%20friend%20Umar%20Khalid%20is%20languishing%20in%20jail.%20Similarly%2C%20many%20Kashmiri%20journalists%2C%20human%20rights%20activists%2C%20and%20other%20innocent%20people%20are%20in%20jails%20without%20any%20trial%20and%20under%20trumped%20up%20charges%20of%20UAPA.%20Father%20Stan%20Swamy%20passed%20away%20in%20jail%20facing%20a%20false%20and%20politically%20motivated%20case%20in%20the%20Bhima%20Koregaon%20matter%20and%20was%20not%20even%20provided%20with%20a%20straw%20to%20eat%20food.%20Fatima%20Nafees%20is%20still%20fighting%20to%20find%20her%20son.%20Radhika%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eamma%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0is%20still%20battling%20all%20odds%20to%20get%20justice%20for%20Rohith%20Vemula.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20surprises%20me%20is%20that%20you%20were%20part%20of%20all%20these%20movements.%20Not%20only%20these%20but%20many%20more.%20It%20is%20this%20heartlessness%20where%20I%20wish%20to%20draw%20a%20line.%20The%20way%20you%20whitewashed%20the%20crimes%20of%20Modi%20and%20Shah%20by%20praising%20them%20for%20being%20%E2%80%9Cselfless%E2%80%9D%20cannot%20just%20be%20a%20change%20of%20heart.%20For%20their%20histories%20to%20be%20forgiven%20and%20forgotten%2C%20for%20which%20there%20has%20never%20been%20remorse%2C%20requires%20not%20a%20change%20of%20heart%20but%20maybe%20an%20absence%20of%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20who%20faced%20witch%20hunts%2C%20unable%20to%20fight%20for%20whatever%20reasons%2C%20either%20became%20silent%2C%20left%20the%20country%20or%20figured%20out%20a%20way%20to%20stay%20out%20of%20the%20political%20path.%20Yet%2C%20they%20did%20not%20turn%20into%20supporters%20of%20what%20is%20a%20palpably%20fascist%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20podcast%2C%20you%20spoke%20about%20a%20flirtation%20with%20revolutionary%20politics%20in%20your%2020s.%20Well%2C%20what%20made%20journalist%20Smita%20Prakash%20sit%20with%20you%20and%20give%20value%20to%20your%20opinions%20is%20this%20very%20flirtation%20with%20revolutionary%20politics%20and%20the%20sacrifices%20of%20hundreds%20and%20thousands%20of%20students%20on%20which%20it%20is%20founded.%20Remember%20that%20Bhagat%20Singh%20was%20in%20his%2020s%20when%20he%20was%20martyred%20fighting%20for%20the%20nation.%20There%20are%20hundreds%20of%20such%20examples%20in%20our%20freedom%20movement%2C%20post-independence%2C%20and%20from%20the%20campus%20you%20graduated.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20tell%20you%20the%20story%20of%20Chandrashekar%20Prasad%2C%20twice-elected%20JNUSU%20President%20who%20was%20killed%20by%20feudal%20goons%20for%20fighting%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20landless%20people.%20By%20the%20way%2C%20he%20was%20in%20his%2020s%20too.%20It%20is%20the%20cynical%20and%20corrupted%20who%20find%20the%20revolutionary%20zeal%20of%20those%20in%20their%2020s%20mere%20%E2%80%98idealistic%E2%80%99.%20To%20dismiss%20the%20honesty%20of%20this%20spirit%2C%20as%20you%20have%20done%2C%20is%20to%20demean%20and%20insult%20the%20struggles%20and%20movements%20of%20students%20in%20universities%2C%20the%20very%20movements%20that%20have%20contributed%20to%20your%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20you%20term%20your%20interactions%20and%20time%20with%20many%20of%20us%20as%20%E2%80%98being%20in%20an%20echo%20chamber%E2%80%99%20only%20made%20me%20question%20my%20own%20earlier%20appreciation%20of%20your%20intelligence%2C%20political%20acumen%2C%20and%20nuanced%20articulations.%20Again%2C%20let%20me%20remind%20you%2C%20that%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%98echo%20chamber%E2%80%99%20helped%20you%20shape%20your%20opinions%20and%20positions%20which%20the%20people%20resisting%20fascism%20welcomed%20with%20open%20hearts.%20Now%20to%20turn%20around%20and%20be%20dismissive%20only%20shows%20you%20are%20capable%20of%20disowning%20anything%2C%20if%20need%20be.%20What%20guarantee%20is%20it%20that%20once%20the%20current%20regime%20is%20defeated%2C%20you%20won%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20change%20of%20heart%20again%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20this%20zeal%20is%20not%20restricted%20to%20the%2020s.%20May%20I%20remind%20you%20that%20Father%20Stan%20Swamy%20was%20not%20in%20his%2020s%2C%20nor%20are%20Fatima%20Nafees%20(Najeeb%E2%80%99s%20mother)%2C%20Radhika%20Amma%20(Rohith%E2%80%99s%20Mother)%2C%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20(%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0editor)%2C%20Paranjoy%20Guha%20Thakurta%2C%20and%20many%20others%20who%20are%20fighting%20for%20justice%20and%20are%20hounded%20for%20exposing%20crony%20capitalism%20of%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlease%20have%20the%20courage%20to%20face%20the%20reality%20that%20your%20past%20association%20with%20left%20and%20progressive%20movements%20may%20be%20coming%20in%20the%20way%20of%20your%20future%20aspirations%2C%20and%20that%20you%20need%20to%20part%20ways%20%E2%80%93%20which%20you%20actually%20did%20a%20long%20time%20ago.%20We%20understood%20and%20never%20pointed%20fingers.%20However%2C%20if%20your%20compulsions%20or%20aspirations%20require%20insulting%20those%20very%20movements%2C%20then%20difficult%20questions%20will%20be%20asked%20about%20your%20change%20of%20heart.%20Is%20it%20really%20a%20change%20of%20heart%20or%20a%20change%20of%20direction%20in%20which%20the%20heart%20wishes%20to%20see%20some%20things%20and%20also%20%E2%80%98unsee%E2%80%99%20much%20more%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20these%20twisted%20ethical%20and%20political%20positions%20that%20are%20enabling%20fundamentalists%20to%20destroy%20India%20that%20I%20find%20difficult%20to%20come%20to%20terms%20with.%20Many%20people%20have%20written%20and%20are%20saying%20that%20there%20must%20be%20some%20compulsions%20and%20pressures%20on%20you%20to%20take%20this%20drastic%20step.%20Well%2C%20if%20a%20common%20citizen%2C%20who%20is%20just%20going%20about%20their%20life%20who%20is%20facing%20the%20music%20of%20unemployment%2C%20harassment%2C%20price%20rise%2C%20and%20others%20is%20still%20resisting%2C%20voting%2C%20and%20fighting%20to%20keep%20BJP%20away%2C%20a%20lot%20is%20expected%20from%20people%20like%20us%20who%20have%20been%20part%20of%20the%20student%20and%20anti-fascist%20movements%20and%20have%20benefited%20from%20critical%20scholarship.%20It%20is%20here%20that%20you%20gave%20up%20and%20decided%20to%20turn%20sides.%20It%20is%20disheartening%20but%20not%20demotivating%2C%20as%20there%20are%20millions%20still%20resisting%20the%20BJP%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20present%20times%2C%20as%20a%20young%20research%20scholar%2C%20one%20just%20has%20to%20go%20to%20a%20job%20interview%20at%20Delhi%20University%20to%20see%20the%20consequences%20of%20commitment%20to%20a%20secular%2C%20socialist%2C%20democratic%2C%20and%20egalitarian%20nation.%20People%20are%20risking%20their%20careers%2C%20taking%20positions%20they%20are%20over-qualified%20for%20just%20because%20they%20opposed%20the%20ABVP.%20Yet%2C%20they%20are%20standing%20strong%20and%20refusing%20to%20give%20in%20to%20get%20a%20job.%20These%20are%20inspiring%20people%20to%20me%3B%20I%20find%20motivation%20to%20strive%20more%20and%20be%20upright%20in%20what%20we%20do%20in%20life.%20I%20find%20inspiration%20in%20people%20who%20refuse%20to%20strike%20bargains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20I%20am%20not%20in%20my%2020s%20anymore%2C%20so%20please%20ignore%20my%20opinion%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EN.%20Sai%20Balaji%20is%20a%20former%20president%20of%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20Students%E2%80%99%20Union%20(JNUSU).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700800210000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F06164543%2FIMG_20190705_124249_524-e1566475547700.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fheartlessness-is-systemic-and-dangerous-a-letter-to-shehla-rashid%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Many%20people%20who%20faced%20witch%20hunts%2C%20unable%20to%20fight%20for%20whatever%20reasons%2C%20either%20became%20silent%2C%20left%20the%20country%20or%20figured%20out%20a%20way%20to%20stay%20out%20of%20the%20political%20path.%20Yet%2C%20they%20did%20not%20turn%20into%20supporters%20of%20what%20is%20a%20palpably%20fascist%20front.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A94%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fheartlessness-is-systemic-and-dangerous-a-letter-to-shehla-rashid%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20New%20Pathogen%2C%20WHO's%20Line%2C%20Why%20China%3F%3A%20What%20We%20Know%20About%20the%20'Unknown%20Pneumonia'%20Outbreak%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24092504%2F6838768118_4231c20017_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Amid%20an%20ongoing%20and%20fresh%20outbreak%20of%20what%20has%20emerged%20as%20%E2%80%9Cunknown%20pneumonia%E2%80%9D%20in%20China%20leading%20to%20crowding%20at%20healthcare%20facilities%20in%20northern%20China%2C%20the%20government%20of%20the%20country%20has%20ruled%20out%20the%20presence%20of%20any%20new%20or%20unknown%20pathogen.%20This%2C%20at%20least%20as%20of%20now%2C%20should%20put%20to%20rest%20fears%20of%20a%20bigger%20outbreak%20which%20could%20have%20pandemic%20potential.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EQuoting%20official%20conversation%20with%20Chinese%20health%20authorities%20from%20the%20Chinese%20Center%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%2C%20and%20the%20Beijing%20Children%E2%80%99s%20Hospital%2C%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20said%20on%20November%2023%20that%20the%20upsurge%20in%20hospital%20admissions%20of%20children%20were%20due%20to%20Mycoplasma%20Pneumoniae%20%E2%80%93%20a%20bacterial%20infection%20%E2%80%93%20from%20May%3B%20and%20Respiratory%20Syncytial%20Virus%20(RSV)%2C%20adenovirus%20and%20influenza%20%E2%80%93%20all%20viral%20infections%20%E2%80%93%20from%20October%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20these%20bacterial%20and%20viral%20infections%20are%20well%20known%20and%20treatments%20to%20these%20are%20available%20%E2%80%93%20unlike%20in%20case%20of%20a%20novel%20pathogen%20(a%20virus%20or%20bacteria).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20recent%20outbreak%20in%20China%20brought%20back%20eerie%20memories%20of%20the%20Sars-Cov-2%20(novel%20coronavirus)%20outbreak.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20also%20described%20as%20pneumonia%20of%20%E2%80%9Cunknown%20aetiology%20(unknown%20cause)%E2%80%9D%20in%20one%20of%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Femergencies%2Fdisease-outbreak-news%2Fitem%2F2020-DON229%23%3A~%3Atext%3DDescription%2520of%2520the%2520Situation%2CCity%252C%2520Hubei%2520Province%2520of%2520China.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20first%20statements%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eof%20the%20WHO%20that%20was%20published%20after%20the%20outbreak%20of%20COVID-19.%20But%20now%2C%20the%20role%20of%20any%20unknown%20pathogen%20has%20been%20ruled%20out%2C%20at%20least%2C%20for%20the%20time%20being%2C%20while%20accepting%20the%20surge%20in%20cases.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%5BThe%5D%20Chinese%20authorities%20advised%20that%20there%20has%20been%20no%20detection%20of%20any%20unusual%20or%20novel%20pathogens%20or%20unusual%20clinical%20presentations%2C%20including%20in%20Beijing%20and%20Liaoning%2C%20but%20only%20the%20aforementioned%20general%20increase%20in%20respiratory%20illnesses%20due%20to%20multiple%20known%20pathogens%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20WHO%20has%20said%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20November%2022%2C%20a%20day%20earlier%2C%20the%20WHO%20made%20its%20first%20formal%20statement%20regarding%20the%20outbreak%20in%20China.%20Various%20images%20circulated%20on%20social%20media%20in%20which%20hospitals%2C%20especially%20treating%20children%2C%20were%20shown%20to%20be%20overwhelmed.%20In%20the%20November%2022%20statement%2C%20the%20WHO%20had%20said%20it%20had%20sought%20more%20information%20from%20China.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20WHO%20move%20was%20necessitated%20by%20a%20report%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpromedmail.org%2Fpromed-post%2F%3Fplace%3D8713261%2C353%23promedmailmap%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EProMed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20November%2021%20which%20spoke%20of%20undiagnosed%20pneumonia%20epidemics%20going%20on%20in%20China.%20ProMed%20is%20an%20international%20forum%20that%20identifies%20infectious%20diseases%20outbreaks%20globally%2C%20and%20is%20usually%20the%20first%20platform%20to%20alert%20the%20global%20scientific%20community%20about%20them%20%E2%80%93%20as%20it%20did%20for%20Covid-19.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20the%20outbreak%20of%20pneumonia%20in%20China%2C%20children%E2%80%99s%20hospitals%20in%20Beijing%2C%20Liaoning%20and%20other%20places%20were%20overwhelmed%20with%20sick%20children%2C%20and%20schools%20and%20classes%20were%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20suspension%2C%E2%80%9D%20ProMed%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20WHO%20wanted%20to%20know%20whether%20there%20were%20%E2%80%9Cclusters%E2%80%9D%20of%20%E2%80%9Cundiagnosed%20pneumonia%E2%80%9D%20in%20Beijing%20and%20Liaoning%20and%20if%20the%20current%20outbreak%20was%20a%20general%20pattern%20of%20increase%20in%20respiratory%20illnesses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Could%20be%20RSV%20or%20HMPV%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20three%20experts%20and%20all%20of%20them%2C%20by%20and%20large%2C%20made%20observations%20similar%20to%20the%20WHO%E2%80%99s%20latest%20statement%20on%20the%20current%20outbreak.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20there%20are%20children%20%5Bwho%20are%20mostly%20infected%5D%2C%20it%20could%20be%20RSV%20or%20Human%20Metapneumovirus%20(HMPV)%20%E2%80%93%20both%20known%20to%20cause%20respiratory%20illness%20in%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shahid%20Jameel%2C%20a%20virologist.%20Jameel%20is%20currently%20a%20research%20fellow%20at%20the%20Oxford%20University%E2%80%99s%20Green%20Templeton%20College.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERSV%2C%20according%20to%20the%20US%20Centers%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%20(US-CDC)%20is%20a%20common%20viral%20respiratory%20infection%20that%20usually%20causes%20mild%2C%20cold-like%20symptoms%20and%20people%20can%20recover%20in%20a%20week%20with%20or%20without%20use%20of%20antibiotics.%20However%2C%20some%20serious%20cases%20may%20require%20hospitalisation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20Mycoplasma%20Pneumonia%20is%20a%20bacterial%20respiratory%20system%20which%20is%20usually%20considered%20mild%20but%20serious%20cases%20be%20hospitalised.%20Both%20of%20them%20are%20transmitted%20through%20droplets%20of%20an%20infected%20person%20or%20a%20close%20contact%20with%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20have%20been%20RSV%20outbreaks%20elsewhere%20%5Balso%20apart%20from%20China%20%5Dafter%20good%20years%20due%20to%20quarantine%20and%20other%20restrictions%20%5Bbeing%20lifted%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jameel%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20WHO%20also%20said%20something%20similar.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20of%20these%20increases%20are%20earlier%20in%20the%20season%20than%20historically%20experienced%2C%20but%20not%20unexpected%20given%20the%20lifting%20of%20COVID-19%20restrictions%2C%20as%20similarly%20experienced%20in%20other%20countries%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20explained.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmesh%20Adalja%2C%20a%20senior%20scholar%20at%20Johns%20Hopkins%20Center%20for%20Health%20Security%2C%20says%20the%20current%20outbreak%20in%20China%20seemed%20to%20mimic%20what%20happened%20in%20the%20US%20earlier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20appears%20that%20this%20outbreak%20is%20likely%20the%20result%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eseveral%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20known%20respiratory%20pathogens%2C%20including%20Mycoplasma%20Pneumoniae%2C%20all%20attacking%20at%20once%20%E2%80%94%20similar%20to%20what%20happened%20in%20the%20US%20last%20year%20with%20simultaneous%20outbreaks%20of%20RSV%2C%20influenza%2C%20and%20COVID-19%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20an%20emailed%20response%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20now%3F%20Why%20China%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIncidentally%2C%20China%20had%20followed%20what%20was%20called%20%E2%80%98Zero%20Covid%E2%80%99%20policy.%20It%20locked%20up%2C%20as%20per%20stringent%20measures%20of%20lockdown%20for%20COVID-19%2C%20large%20swathes%20of%20the%20population%20for%20a%20very%20long%20time%20%E2%80%93%20longer%20than%20many%20other%20countries.%20This%20resulted%20in%20a%20scenario%20in%20which%20the%20population%20didn%E2%80%99t%20get%20exposed%20to%20other%20respiratory%20viruses%20or%20bacteria%20also%2C%20in%20the%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0And%2C%20once%20the%20measures%20were%20lifted%20this%20winter%2C%C2%A0%20this%20population%20got%20exposed%20to%20all%20of%20them%20leading%20to%20the%20surge%20in%20cases.%20Moreover%2C%20not%20getting%20exposed%20to%20these%20pathogens%20for%20a%20long%20time%20could%20also%20have%20created%20what%20is%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98immunological%20deficit%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20a%20deficiency%20in%20natural%20immunity%20acquired%20against%20the%20pathogens%20due%20to%20exposure%20to%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBharat%20Pankhania%2C%20an%20infectious%20diseases%20expert%20with%20University%20of%20Exter%20Medical%20School%2C%20UK%2C%20believes%20the%20%E2%80%98deficit%E2%80%99%20might%20not%20provide%20the%20complete%20answer%20to%20the%20ongoing%20outbreak.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CImmunological%20deficit%20is%20not%20surprising%E2%80%A6but%20then%20you%20can%20have%20more%20people%20infected%20than%20expected%20because%20of%20circumstances%20like%20crowded%20schools%2C%20crowded%20shops%2C%20buses%2C%20trains%E2%80%A6and%20there%20is%20winter%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20it%E2%80%99s%20very%20difficult%20to%20disentangle%20%5Bwhether%5D%20it%20is%20an%20immunological%20deficit%2C%20or%20is%20it%20environmental%20circumstances.%20Or%20perhaps%20both%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENonetheless%2C%20Pankhania%20stressed%20that%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20patients%20responding%20to%20the%20drugs%20in%20this%20outbreak%20is%20a%20pointer%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20is%20not%20an%20unknown%20infection.%20The%20Chinese%20authorities%2C%20per%20WHO%2C%20have%20also%20said%20there%20is%20no%20change%20in%20the%20presentation%20of%20these%20diseases%20vis-a-vis%20the%20patterns%20already%20known.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20next%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECurrently%2C%20going%20by%20the%20data%20provided%20by%20the%20Chinese%20authorities%2C%20the%20WHO%20has%20assessed%20that%20the%20outbreak%20of%20the%20respiratory%20illnesses%20are%20caused%20by%20the%20known%20pathogens%20which%20are%20readily%20treatable%20with%20antibiotics%2C%20if%20needed.%20And%2C%20therefore%2C%20there%20was%20no%20cause%20of%20immediate%20alarm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20Pankhania%20and%20Adalja%20said%20the%20Chinese%20authorities%20must%20share%20data%20with%20the%20global%20scientific%20community.%20They%20must%C2%A0%20publish%20the%20detailed%20findings%20of%20their%20inquiry%20besides%20sharing%20genome%20sequences%20of%20the%20samples%20tested.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20WHO%20has%20also%20added%20though%20information%20available%20is%20%E2%80%9Climited%E2%80%9D%20to%20%E2%80%9Cfully%20characterise%E2%80%9D%20the%20overall%20risk%20even%20though%20winter%20season%20is%20known%20to%20create%20a%20spike%20in%20respiratory%20infections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20sounding%20a%20cautionary%20note%2C%20it%20said%20it%20will%20continue%20to%20closely%20monitor%20the%20situation%20and%20would%20be%20in%20close%20contact%20with%20national%20authorities%20of%20China.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700798192000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24092504%2F6838768118_4231c20017_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fchina-pneumonia-outbreak-who-pandemic%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chinese%C2%A0authorities%20told%20the%20WHO%20that%20the%20current%20outbreak%20is%C2%A0related%20to%20'already%20known'%20viruses%20or%20bacteria%2C%20thus%20ruling%20out%20any%20potential%20pandemic.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fchina-pneumonia-outbreak-who-pandemic%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'We%20are%20drowning%20here'%3A%20Gazan%20doctors%20appeal%20for%20help%20after%20IDF%20arrests%20hospital%20chief%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700780100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F11%2F768x432%2Fskynews-injured-child-gaza-european-hospital_6370129.jpg%3F20231124000642%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fisrael-hamas-war-gazan-doctors-appeal-for-help-after-idf-arrests-hospital-chief-13014688%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Doctors%20in%20Gaza%20have%20appealed%20for%20international%20help%20after%20the%20arrest%20of%20the%20director%20of%20al%20Shifa%20hospital%20by%20the%20Israel%20Defence%20Forces%20(IDF).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A547%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fisrael-hamas-war-gazan-doctors-appeal-for-help-after-idf-arrests-hospital-chief-13014688%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fisrael-hamas-war-gazan-doctors-appeal-for-help-after-idf-arrests-hospital-chief-13014688%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fisrael